h%20Yadav%2C%20who%20was%20named%20in%20an%20FIR%20by%20Noida%20Police%20for%20allegedly%20supplying%20snake%20venom%20at%20rave%20parties%2C%20denied%20the%20charges%20and%20pledged%20cooperation%20with%20the%20UP%20Police.%20Maneka%20Gandhi%20demanded%20his%20immediate%20arrest%2C%20stating%20that%20owning%2C%20catching%2C%20or%20using%20snakes%20is%20a%20wildlife%20crime.%20PETA%20India%20also%20condemned%20Elvish%20Yadav%2C%20highlighting%20the%20cruelty%20faced%20by%20snakes%20in%20such%20situations.%20Take%20a%20look%3A%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22etimes.in%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kalakshetra%3A%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20Steps%20Down%20as%20Director%2C%20Aneish%20Rajan%20Takes%20Charge%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03135327%2FF96u2jba4AALEnM.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EMonths%20after%20allegations%20of%20sexual%20harassment%20and%20abuse%20surfaced%20at%20Chennai%E2%80%99s%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation%2C%20director%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20has%20stepped%20down%20from%20office.%20She%20will%20be%20replaced%20by%20Aneish%20Rajan%2C%20deputy%20secretary%20at%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Culture.%C2%A0%20Kalakshetra%20announced%20the%20transfer%20of%20power%20on%20Thursday%2C%20November%202%20on%20their%20social%20media%20handles.%20Sources%20in%20Kalakshetra%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Aneish%20was%20taking%20over%20only%20as%20an%20acting%20director%2C%20but%20this%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20confirmed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20change%20of%20directors%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20allegations%20of%20harassment%20at%20the%20Rukmini%20Devi%20College%20of%20Fine%20Arts%20(RDFCA)%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation.%20Though%20the%20allegations%20surfaced%20in%20December%20of%20last%20year%2C%20students%20battled%20with%20the%20administration%20for%20months%20before%20their%20complaints%20were%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20inquiry%20committee%20helmed%20by%20retired%20judge%20Justice%20K.%20Kannan%2C%20and%20comprising%20of%20former%20Tamil%20Nadu%20director%20general%20of%20police%20(DGP)%20Letika%20Saran%20and%20Shobha%20Varthaman%2C%20set%20up%20by%20S.%20Ramadorai%2C%20chairman%20of%20the%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation%20in%20April%202023%2C%20recommended%20that%20able%20administrators%20with%20%E2%80%9Cbackground%20in%20human%20resources%20management%20and%20organisational%20skills%2C%20with%20a%20high%20level%20of%20interest%20in%20performing%20arts%20as%20additional%20interest%2C%20shall%20alone%20be%20considered%20for%20the%20posts%20of%20the%20chief%20functionaries%2C%20such%20as%20Director%20and%20Principal%20of%20the%20Institution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ESmt.%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20has%20demitted%20the%20charge%20of%20Director%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkalakshetrafdn%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40kalakshetrafdn%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20October%2031%2C%202023.%20Shri%20Aneish%20Rajan%2C%20has%20taken%20over%20as%20Director%20(IC)%20from%20November%2001%2C%202023%2C%20with%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20Governing%20Board%20members%20and%20Advisor%20present%20during%20the%20occasion.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FioXCT9Jml5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FioXCT9Jml5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Kalakshetra%20India%20(%40kalakshetrafdn)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fkalakshetrafdn%2Fstatus%2F1720004710458171839%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3ENovember%202%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EAniesh%20Rajan%20is%20a%20former%20Revenue%20Service%20Officer%20(IRS)%20who%20had%20previously%20served%20as%20the%20Kerala%20Customs%20Department%20Joint%20Commissioner%20before%20he%20became%20deputy%20secretary%20in%202022.%20His%20service%20as%20the%20joint%20commissioner%20was%20marred%20at%20the%20time%20by%20accusations%20of%20a%20political%20nature%20during%20the%20high-profile%20Thiruvananthapuram%20gold%20smuggling%20case%2C%20and%20Aneish%20was%20then%20transferred%20from%20Kochi%20to%20Nagpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20protests%20in%20Kalakshetra%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStudents%20of%20RDFCA%20had%20come%20forward%20with%20sexual%20harassment%20allegations%20against%20senior%20faculty%20Hari%20Padman%20and%20three%20members%20of%20the%20repertory%20%E2%80%94%20Sanjith%20Lal%2C%20Sai%20Krishnan%2C%20and%20Srinath.%20Following%20this%2C%20on%20March%2031%2C%20they%20staged%20a%20night-long%20protest%20demanding%20action%20against%20the%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EHari%20Padman%20was%20finally%20arrested%20on%20April%203%20after%20an%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20him%20at%20the%20Adyar%20All%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Police%20Station%20(AWPS).%20He%20was%20released%20on%20bail%20in%20June.%20Meanwhile%2C%20no%20legal%20action%20has%20been%20taken%20so%20far%20against%20the%20other%20three%20accused.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20course%20of%20the%20student%20and%20public%20outcry%2C%20two%20survivors%20and%20six%20staff%20members%20spoke%20to%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20in%20March%202023%2C%20detailing%20how%20the%20atmosphere%20at%20the%20Kalakshetra%20campus%20was%20toxic.%20The%20survivors%20told%20%3Cem%3ETNM%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20Hari%20Padman%20would%20invite%20them%20to%20his%20residence%20within%20the%20campus%2C%20and%20denying%20his%20advances%20invited%20severe%20humiliation%20and%20repercussions%2C%20even%20leading%20to%20some%20women%20quitting%20their%20course%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EStudents%20had%20also%20told%20TNM%20that%20their%20appeals%20for%20justice%20to%20Revathi%20Ramachandran%20had%20been%20dismissed%20outright%20or%20not%20given%20due%20importance.%20Moreover%2C%20students%20and%20faculty%20members%20have%20also%20said%20that%20the%20atmosphere%20on%20campus%20was%20casteist%20and%20misogynistic%20with%20women%20students%20constantly%20under%20the%20scanner.%20It%20also%20came%20to%20light%20that%20Revathi%20had%20allegedly%20covered%20up%20a%20mass%20outbreak%20of%20food%20poisoning%20on%20campus%20from%20the%20hostel%20food%20in%202021%20during%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic.%20When%20students%20became%20vocal%20about%20the%20attempted%20cover-up%2C%20they%20allegedly%20faced%20more%20retaliation%20from%20Revathi%20who%20accused%20them%20of%20%E2%80%9Cpainting%20her%20in%20a%20bad%20light.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20April%20this%20year%2C%20a%20transwoman%20alumna%20of%20the%20RDCFA%20wrote%20to%20the%20Tamil%20Nadu%20State%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Commission%20(SWC)%20%3Cins%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Fkalakshetra-alumna-alleges-sexual-assault-governing-board-member-writes-swc-176341%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elodging%20a%20complaint%20of%20sexual%20assault%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3C%2Fins%3Eand%20transphobia%20against%20several%20Kalakshetra%20employees%20including%20current%20governing%20board%20member%20P.T.%20Narendran.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20inquiry%20committee%20found%20Hari%20Padman%20guilty%20of%20gross%20misconduct%20and%20suggested%20that%20the%20students%20who%20complained%20of%20sexual%20misbehaviour%20by%20Sanjith%20Lal%2C%20Saikrishna%2C%20and%20Srinath%2C%20be%20provided%20with%20legal%20assistance%20to%20file%20police%20complaints.%20The%20report%20further%20says%20that%20any%20sexual%20intent%20of%20the%20teacher%20to%20a%20student%20is%20an%20abhorrent%20expression%20of%20asymmetry%20of%20power.%20It%20also%20recommended%20the%20establishment%20of%20a%20students%E2%80%99%20grievances%20redressal%20committee%2C%20as%20contemplated%20by%20the%20University%20Grants%20Commission%20(UGC)%20Regulations%20of%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%20data-test-id%3D%5C%22text%5C%22%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20contents%20of%20the%20report%2C%20which%20was%20written%20many%20months%20ago%2C%20remain%20unpublished%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2Ftamil-nadu%2Frevathi-ramachandran-steps-down-as-director-of-kalakshetra-aneish-rajan-takes-charge%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20originally%20published%20by%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thenewsminute.com%2F%5C%22%3EThe%20News%20Minute%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699003773000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03135327%2FF96u2jba4AALEnM.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkalakshetra-revathi-ramachandran-director-aneish-rajan%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20change%20comes%20in%20the%20wake%20of%20allegations%20of%20harassment%20at%20the%20Rukmini%20Devi%20College%20of%20Fine%20Arts%2C%20which%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20Kalakshetra%20Foundation.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fthe-arts%2Fkalakshetra-revathi-ramachandran-director-aneish-rajan%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Pisa%20floods%20as%20Storm%20Ciar%C3%A1n%20strikes%20Tuscany%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699003572000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F03B6%2Fproduction%2F_131605900_p0gqj9rz.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-67307070%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20least%20three%20people%20were%20killed%20as%20the%