EThe%20CBI%20arrested%20Sisodia%20on%20February%2026%2C%20charging%20him%20with%20taking%20a%20bribe%20for%20tweaking%20the%20excise%20policy%20of%20the%20Delhi%20government%20to%20favour%20a%20liquor%20lobby.%20On%20March%208%2C%20the%20ED%20formally%20charged%20Sisodia%20under%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA).%20Since%20then%2C%20Sisodia%20has%20been%20in%20prison.%20From%20the%20lower%20courts%20up%20to%20the%20Delhi%20High%20Court%2C%20he%E2%80%99s%20been%20denied%20bail.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EJustice%20Khanna%2C%20presiding%20over%20a%20two-judge%20bench%20which%20included%20Justice%20S.V.N.%20Bhatti%2C%20pointed%20out%20that%20as%20per%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20the%20recipient%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20crime%20was%20%E2%80%9Ca%20political%20party%E2%80%9D%20and%20not%20Sisodia%2C%20and%20asked%20why%20the%20party%20was%20not%20made%20an%20accused.%20%E2%80%9CAs%20far%20as%20the%20Prevention%20of%20Money%20Laundering%20Act%20(PMLA)%20is%20concerned%2C%20your%20whole%20case%20is%20that%20it%20went%20to%20a%20political%20party.%20That%20political%20party%20is%20still%20not%20an%20accused.%20How%20do%20you%20answer%20that%3F%20He%20is%20not%20the%20beneficiary%2C%20the%20political%20party%20is%20the%20beneficiary%2C%E2%80%9D%20Justice%20Khanna%20had%20stated%20then.%20On%20October%2017%2C%20repeating%20the%20same%20line%2C%20after%20arguments%20were%20concluded%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20announced%20that%20the%20verdict%20on%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20plea%20would%20be%20delivered%20on%20October%2030.%C2%A0%20Following%20this%2C%20the%20ED%20told%20the%20media%20that%20it%20was%20contemplating%20making%20AAP%20an%20accused%20in%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOn%20October%2030%2C%20Justice%20Khanna%20wrote%20the%20verdict%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fsupreme-court-manish-sisodia-bail%5C%22%3Erejecting%20Manish%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20while%20raising%20%E2%80%9Csome%20doubts%E2%80%9D%20about%20some%20of%20the%20charges%20levelled%20by%20the%20ED.%20He%20refrained%20%E2%80%9Cfrom%20delving%E2%80%A6%20in%20depth%20and%20detail%20into%20some%20of%20the%20legal%20questions%20arising%20in%20the%20matter%20and%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CHowever%20there%20is%20one%20clear%20ground%20or%20charge%20in%20the%20complaint%20filed%20under%20the%20PMLA%20which%20is%20free%20from%20perceptible%20legal%20challenge%20and%20the%20facts%20as%20alleged%20are%20tentatively%20supported%20by%20material%20evidence.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDuring%20arguments%20Justice%20Khanna%2C%20leading%20the%20bench%2C%20had%20warned%20that%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20claims%20against%20Sisodia%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20fall%20flat%E2%80%9D%20after%20%E2%80%9Ctwo%20questions%20in%20the%20cross-examination.%E2%80%9D%20The%20ED%20had%20contended%20that%20the%20CBI%20investigating%20the%20alleged%20act%20of%20corruption%20had%20claimed%20that%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%202.2%20crore%20was%20paid%20by%20Amit%20Arora%20through%20middleman%20Dinesh%20Arora.%20The%20bench%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20%E2%80%9Cis%20not%20a%20charge%20or%20an%20allegation%20made%20in%20the%20chargesheet%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%E2%80%9D%20and%20%E2%80%9Cit%20may%20be%20difficult%20to%20regard%20alleged%20payment%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cproceed%20of%20crime%20under%20the%20PMLA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20ED%20had%20claimed%20that%20part%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20the%20crime%20were%20used%20to%20fund%20the%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20poll%20campaign%20in%20Goa.%20However%2C%20the%20bench%20noted%20that%20the%20agency%20said%20that%20%E2%80%9Conce%20the%20quantum%20of%20amount%20used%20in%20the%20election%20in%20Goa%20is%20ascertained%2C%20a%20decision%20to%20consider%20AAP%20as%20an%20accused%20under%20Section%203%20of%20the%20PMLA%20will%20be%20taken.%E2%80%9D%20Goa%20Assembly%20elections%20were%20held%20in%20February%2C%202022.%20But%20it%20is%20evident%20from%20whatever%20the%20ED%20stated%20in%20the%20apex%20court%20that%20after%20more%20than%2020%20months%20the%20ED%20has%20no%20idea%20how%20much%20the%20AAP%20spent%20on%20the%20Goa%20Assembly%20elections.%20And%20so%20there%20is%20no%20substance%20in%20its%20charge.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20had%20also%20pointed%20out%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20charge%20that%E2%80%A6Sisodia%20is%20vicariously%20liable%20in%20terms%20of%20Section%2070%20of%20the%20PMLA%20cannot%20be%20alleged%20and%20has%20not%20been%20argued.%E2%80%9D%20The%20bench%20mentioned%20that%20%E2%80%9Cprima%20facie%20there%20is%20lack%20of%20clarity%2C%20as%20specific%20allegation%20on%20the%20involvement%20of%20%E2%80%A6Sisodia%2C%20direct%20or%20indirect%2C%20in%20the%20transfer%20of%20Rs%2045%20crore%20to%20AAP%20for%20Goa%20elections%20is%20missing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20further%20noted%20that%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20allegation%20that%20kickback%20of%20Rs%20100%20crore%20%E2%80%9Cwas%20actually%20paid%20by%20the%20liquor%20group%20is%20somewhat%20a%20matter%20of%20debate%2C%20questioning%20also%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20contention%E2%80%A6%20that%20generation%20of%20proceeds%20of%20crime%20is%20itself%20possession%20or%20use%20of%20the%20proceeds%20of%20crime.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAll%20the%20questions%20the%20bench%20raised%20and%20observations%20it%20made%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20arguments%20clearly%20demonstrated%20that%20it%20found%20no%20substance%20or%20strength%20in%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20case%20against%20Sisodia.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESisodia%20has%20been%20in%20jail%20for%20the%20last%20eight%20months%2C%20despite%20the%20bench%20finding%20a%20very%20untenable%20case%20against%20the%20AAP%20leader.%20But%20on%20October%2030%2C%20when%20Justice%20Khanna%20delivered%20the%20judgement%2C%20it%20went%20totally%20against%20the%20kernel%20of%20his%20observations%20during%20the%20course%20of%20the%20arguments%20the%20ED%20had%20extended%20on%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20bail%20plea.%20That%20is%20the%20mysterious%20aspect%20of%20this%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20stated%2C%20%E2%80%9CIn%20view%20of%20the%20aforesaid%20discussion%20and%20for%20the%20reasons%20stated%2C%20we%20are%20not%20inclined%20to%20accept%20the%20prayer%20for%20grant%20of%20bail%20at%20this%20stage.%E2%80%9D%20However%2C%20perhaps%20to%20assuage%20Sisodia%E2%80%99s%20hurt%20in%20denial%20of%20bail%2C%20it%20added%20that%20the%20prosecution%20had%20assured%20that%20the%20trial%20would%20be%20completed%20in%20six%20to%20eight%20months%20and%20added%20that%20Sisodia%20could%20file%20a%20fresh%20bail%20application%20if%20the%20trial%20was%20protracted.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20effect%2C%20the%20bench%20ensured%20that%20Sisodia%20is%20not%20let%20out%20on%20bail%20before%20completing%20at%20least%20a%20year%20behind%20bars%2C%20without%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhat%20happened%20between%20October%2017%20and%20October%2030%20that%20despite%20all%20the%20pertinent%20points%20Justice%20Khanna%20had%20made%20against%20the%20ED%20arguments%2C%20he%20suddenly%20found%20merit%20in%20the%20ED%20case%3F%20That%E2%80%99s%20a%20mystery%20that%20should%20engage%20everyone%E2%80%99s%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFaraz%20Ahmad%20is%20a%20senior%20journalist%20based%20in%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20piece%20was%20first%20published%20on%20The%20India%20Cable%20%E2%80%93%20a%20premium%20newsletter%20from%20The%20Wire%20%26amp%3B%20Galileo%20Ideas%20%E2%80%93%20and%20has%20been%20updated%20and%20republished%20here.%20To%20subscribe%20to%20The%20India%20Cable%2C%20click%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22http%3A%2F%2Ftheindiacable.com%2F%5C%22%3Ehere%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699001754000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F08%2F31224356%2FSupreme-Court-II-png.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-supreme-court-bail-justice-khanna%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22What%20happened%20between%20October%2017%20and%20October%2030%