0has%20now%20increased%20to%20over%209000%20in%20three%20weeks.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20one%20of%20the%20few%20countries%20outside%20the%20western%20bloc%20which%20has%20not%20used%20the%20term%20ceasefire%20or%20humanitarian%20pause%20for%20the%20current%20violence%20in%20West%20Asia.%20It%20has%20avoided%20the%20term%20%E2%80%98ceasefire%E2%80%99%2C%20while%20saying%20that%20the%20solution%20has%20to%20be%20found%20through%20negotiation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESimilarly%2C%20Jaishankar%20told%20Italian%20lawmakers%20that%20%E2%80%9Cwhat%20happened%20on%20October%207%20was%20a%20big%20act%20of%20terrorism%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20has%20taken%20the%20entire%20region%20into%20a%20different%20direction.%20But%20surely%2C%20it%20must%20be%20everybody%E2%80%99s%20hope%20that%20eventually%E2%80%A6the%20conflict%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20the%20normal%20of%20the%20region%20and%20that%20it%20comes%20back%20to%20some%20stability%2C%20some%20cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20as%20per%20news%20agency%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EANI%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EStating%20that%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbalance%E2%80%9D%20has%20to%20be%20found%20between%20the%20two%20issues%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CIf%20there%20is%20issue%20of%20terrorism%2C%20and%20we%20all%20find%20terrorism%20unacceptable%2C%20we%20have%20to%20stand%20up.%20But%20there%20is%20also%20an%20issue%20of%20Palestine.%20There%20has%20to%20be%20solution%20for%20the%20problems%20faced%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20reiterated%20that%20%E2%80%9Cdialogue%20and%20negotiations%E2%80%9D%20are%20necessary%20to%20find%20a%20way%20out%20of%20the%20current%20crisis.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9COur%20view%20is%20that%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20If%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution%2C%20you%20have%20to%20find%20a%20solution%20through%20dialogue%20and%20negotiation.%20You%20cannot%20find%20a%20solution%20through%20conflict%20and%20terrorism.%20So%20we%20would%20support%20that%20as%20well.%20Given%20the%20current%20situation%E2%80%A6we%20do%20believe%20that%20humanitarian%20law%20must%20be%20respected.%20In%20any%20complex%20situation%2C%20it%20is%20not%20wise%20to%20not%20get%20the%20balance%20right%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EInternational%20humanitarian%20law%20has%20strict%20prohibitions%20against%20targeting%20of%20civilians%20in%20a%20conflict%20zone.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699001532000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F30123119%2FUntitled-design-4-2.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjaishankar-hamas-israel-india-palestine%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Jaishankar%20said%20that%20while%20terrorism%20was%20%E2%80%9Cunacceptable%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20solution%20had%20to%20be%20also%20found%20for%20the%20%E2%80%9Cproblems%20faced%20by%20the%20Palestinian%20people%E2%80%9D.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fdiplomacy%2Fjaishankar-hamas-israel-india-palestine%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%20debut%2050-year%20bond%20fully%20sold%20on%20increasing%20insurer%20demand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1699001446000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-11%2F03%2Ffull%2F1699001312-6916.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fmarkets%2Fnews%2Findia-debut-50-year-bond-fully-sold-on-increasing-insurer-demand-123110300561_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20government%20sold%20Rs%2010%2C000%20crore%20(%241.2%20billion)%20of%20the%202073%20bond%20at%20a%20cutoff%20yield%20of%207.46%