0%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EIllustration%3A%20Pariplab%20Chakraborty%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThere%20is%20no%20clear%20answer%20as%20to%20how%20they%20originated%20and%20when.%20There%20is%20also%20no%20documentary%20evidence%20to%20pinpoint%20when%20and%20how%20members%20of%20this%20group%20transformed%20into%20a%20Koeri%2FKushwaha.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20legends%20suggests%20that%20the%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20dynasty%20originated%20from%20Ram%E2%80%99s%20son%20Kush%2C%20a%20claim%20not%20found%20in%20any%20text%20and%20which%20can%20only%20be%20considered%20a%20myth.%20The%20fact%20is%20that%20they%20are%20farmers%20even%20today%20and%20farming%20has%20been%20their%20traditional%20occupation.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20at%20some%20places%20they%20have%20also%20been%20described%20as%20Kshatriyas%20and%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20take%20pride%20in%20calling%20themselves%20so.%20But%20the%20definition%20of%20%E2%80%98Kshatriya%20itself%20has%20always%20been%20varied.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20instance%2C%20according%20to%20one%20of%20the%20definitions%2C%20one%20who%20owns%20a%20tract%20of%20land%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekshetra%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20is%20called%20a%20Kshatriya.%20Another%20definition%20given%20by%20Jotirao%20Phule%20in%20his%20classic%20book%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EGulamgiri%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%201873%20states%20that%20the%20Kshatriyas%20were%20actually%20regional%2C%20or%20local%2C%20warriors%20who%20fought%20the%20Aryan%20invaders.%20According%20to%20the%20third%20definition%2C%20which%20is%20the%20most%20prevalent%20today%2C%20a%20Rajput%20is%20a%20Kshatriya%20and%20a%20Kshatriya%20is%20a%20Rajput.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20identity%20of%20the%20Koeri%20caste%20is%20not%20clear%20from%20any%20of%20these%20three%20definitions.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFirst%2C%20they%20do%20not%20have%20enough%20land%20to%20be%20called%20Kshatriyas%2C%20and%20when%20there%20is%20no%20land%2C%20they%20have%20nothing%20to%20protect%20or%20stand%20for.%20Since%20a%20Kshatriya%20is%20someone%20who%20protects%20his%20territory%2C%20how%20can%20they%20be%20called%20Kshatriyas%3F%20The%20definition%20of%20Jotirao%20Phule%20is%20a%20broad%20definition%20and%20it%20is%20possible%20that%20people%20of%20this%20caste%20may%20also%20have%20been%20regional%20warriors%2C%20but%20who%20will%20testify%20to%20it%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnyway%2C%20the%20Indian%20Hindu%20society%20is%20so%20divided%20that%20unity%20is%20not%20possible%20despite%20occupational%20similarities.%20For%20example%2C%20the%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20farming%20but%20so%20are%20people%20of%20some%20other%20castes.%20In%20fact%2C%20Brahmins%2C%20Bhumihars%20and%20Rajputs%20also%20call%20themselves%20farmers.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20their%20farming%20and%20the%20farming%20of%20Koeri%2FKushwahas.%20They%20have%20large%20agricultural%20land%20holdings.%20The%20central%20idea%20of%20land%20reform%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20land%20belongs%20to%20its%20tiller%20%E2%80%93%20does%20not%20hold%20true%20in%20this%20case.%20They%20have%20rights%20over%20land%2C%20but%20do%20not%20cultivate%20it.%20Actual%20farming%20is%20done%20by%20members%20of%20other%20castes%2C%20one%20of%20which%20is%20Koeri%2FKushwaha.%20Similarly%2C%20there%20is%20a%20Kurmi%20caste%20which%20does%20farming.%20They%20do%20not%20have%20many%20land%20holdings%20like%20Brahmins%2C%20Rajputs%20and%20Bhumihars%2C%20but%20they%20certainly%20have%20more%20land%20compared%20to%20Koeris%2C%20Yadavas%2C%20Dangis%2C%20Kushwahas%2C%20Koris%2C%20Kachis%2C%20etc.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EClearly%2C%20despite%20similarities%20in%20nature%20of%20work%2C%20there%20is%20no%20unity%20in%20these%20caste%20groups.%20Even%20if%20a%20classification%20was%20made%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20land%20holding%2C%20one%20might%20assume%20that%20there%20would%20be%20two%20categories%20of%20big%20and%20small%20farmers%20and%20they%20would%20at%20least%20happily%20co-exist%20with%20fellow%20members%20in%20their%20respective%20groups.%20But%20that%20was%20not%20to%20be%20the%20case.%20Even%20Kurmis%20and%20Dangis%20consider%20sitting%20next%20to%20Koeris%20%E2%80%98demeaning.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20in%20spite%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20before%202017%2C%20when%20caste%20certificates%20were%20issued%20to%20Kushwahas%20and%20Dangis%20in%20Bihar%2C%20Koeris%20were%20mentioned%20as%20a%20%E2%80%98caste%E2%80%99%20and%20Kushwahas%20or%20Dangis%20were%20categorised%20as%20%E2%80%98sub-caste.%E2%80%99%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20divide%20is%20also%20visible%20at%20the%20social%20and%20cultural%20level.%20Both%20the%20Dangi%20community%2C%20which%20is%20the%20closest%20in%20status%20to%20the%20Koeris%2C%20and%20the%20Yadav%20community%2C%20which%20is%20a%20only%20a%20little%20ahead%2C%20have%20almost%20the%20same%20nature%20of%20work.%20But%20neither%20the%20Dangis%20nor%20the%20Yadavs%20form%20matrimonial%20alliances%20or%20mix%20with%20the%20Koeris.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Koeris%20have%20been%20an%20important%20section%20of%20the%20society%20in%20Bihar%20for%20many%20reasons.%20One%2C%20the%20Koeri%20caste%20has%20the%20largest%20population%20in%20terms%20of%20numbers.%20According%20to%20the%20Caste%20Based%20Census%20Report-2022%2C%20the%20population%20of%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20in%20Bihar%20is%205%2C506%2C113%20while%20the%20population%20of%20Dangis%20is%20only%20336%2C629.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20an%20updated%20figure%20and%20the%20reason%20why%20it%20has%20been%20released%20is%20also%20very%20interesting.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20present%2C%20the%20political%20game%20in%20our%20democracy%20has%20stepped%20up%20with%20many%20an%20interesting%20strategy%20at%20play.%20Before%202017%2C%20Dangi%20was%20included%20in%20Appendix-2%20of%20the%20backward%20classes%20in%20Bihar%2C%20which%20included%20Yadavs%20and%20Kurmis%20in%20addition%20to%20Koeris.%20But%20in%202017%2C%20Nitish%20Kumar%E2%80%99s%20government%20put%20the%20Dangi%20community%20in%20the%20Appendix-1%20of%20the%20backward%20classes%20and%20tagged%20it%20as%20extremely%20backward%20%E2%80%93%20not%20without%20reason.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEarlier%2C%20apart%20from%20Kushwaha%2FKoeris%2C%20Mali%20(349%2C285)%2C%20Gangota%20(648%2C943)%2C%20and%20others%20formed%20a%20large%20group%2C%20which%20had%20political%20implications.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20outcome%20of%20this%20numerical%20strength%20was%20that%20the%20first%20OBC%20chief%20minister%20in%20Bihar%20%E2%80%93%20Satish%20Prasad%20Singh%20%E2%80%93%20hailed%20from%20this%20community.%20However%2C%20he%20had%20to%20vacate%20the%20chair%20for%20B.P.%20Mandal%20within%20just%20two%20days.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESatish%20Prasad%E2%80%99s%20deputy%20for%20those%20two%20days%2C%20Jagdev%20Prasad%2C%20proved%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20and%20the%20most%20revolutionary%20leader%20of%20this%20caste%20group%20in%20Bihar%2C%20but%20he%20could%20not%20reach%20the%20post%20of%20chief%20minister%20only%20due%20to%20weaker%20numerical%20strength.%20This%20unity%20ended%20after%20his%20assassination%20in%201974%20in%20Kurtha%20block%20of%20Bihar.%20Today%20the%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20community%20is%20engaged%20in%20politics%20of%20the%20region%20while%20the%20Dangis%20are%20also%20not%20lagging%20behind.%20Two%20active%20leaders%20are%20Nagamani%20(the%20son%20of%20Jagdev%20Prasad)%20and%20Bagi%20Prasad%20Verma.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20a%20fact%20that%20due%20to%20the%20Mandal%20movement%2C%20some%20degree%20of%20leadership%20potential%20has%20been%20created%20among%20all%20the%20castes.%20However%2C%20its%20side%20effects%20have%20also%20come%20to%20light.%20Since%20the%20number%20of%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20Koeri%20caste%20group%20is%20large%2C%20their%20political%20demand%20is%20naturally%20large%20too.%20Both%20the%20Bharatiya%20Janata%20Party%20and%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20have%20made%20Samrat%20Chaudhary%20and%20Umesh%20Kushwaha%2C%20who%20come%20from%20Kushwaha%20community%2C%20their%20state%20presidents.%20There%20is%20another%20leader%20who%20has%20made%20a%20distinct%20identity%20in%20Kushwaha%20politics%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbihar-nitish-kumar-upendra-kushwaha-criticism%5C%22%3EUpendra%20Kushwaha.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20people%20of%20Dangi%20community%20take%20pride%20in%20the%20fact%20that%20they%20have%20been%20marked%20%E2%80%98extremely%20backward%E2%80%99%20instead%20of%20%E2%80%98backward%E2%80%99.%20This%20caste%20group%20is%20also%20divided%20into%20Badki%20Dangi%20and%20Chhutki%20Dangi%20depending%20on%20the%20size%20of%20land%20holdings.%20Badki%20Dangis%20have%20big%20land%20holdings%20and%20Chhutki%20Dangis%20have%20small%20land%20holdings.%20However%2C%20there%20is%20another%20difference.%20Despite%20having%20one%20deity%20for%20the%20clan%20(%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Ekuldevta%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E)%2C%20the%20Badki%20Dangis%20consider%20themselves%20better%20than%20the%20rest%20because%20they%20do%20not%20have%20the%20tradition%20of%20widow%20remarriage.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20this%20regard%2C%20former%20member%20of%20Bihar%20legislative%20assembly%20N.K.%20Nanda%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CJagdev%20Prasad%20hailed%20from%20Badki%20Dangi.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20it%20was%20he%20who%20called%20for%20ending%20the%20divide%2C%20or%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshakha%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20between%20the%20two%20Dangi%20groups%20and%20establishing%20matrimonial%20alliances.%20He%20was%20also%20in%20favour%20of%20marriage%20between%20Ahirs%2C%20Kurmis%2C%20Koeris%20and%20Dangis.%20The%20people%20of%20Dangi%20community%20might%20be%20less%20in%20number%2C%20but%20they%20have%20been%20ahead%20of%20the%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20community%20in%20terms%20of%20education%20and%20economic%20condition.%20When%20Jagdev%20Prasad%2C%20despite%20coming%20from%20a%20large%20Dangi%20community%2C%20got%20his%20son%2C%20Senapati%2C%20married%20into%20a%20Koeri%20family%2C%20the%20people%20of%20the%20Dangi%20community%20ostracised%20him%20socially%20while%20the%20Koeri%2FKushwaha%20community%20accepted%20him.%20However%2C%20later%20when%20Prasad%20was%20searching%20for%20a%20place%20to%20reside%20in%20Patna%2C%20the%20people%20of%20Dangi%20community%20in%20Murlichak%20offered%20him%20land.%20Today%2C%20the%20house%20he%20built%2C%20right%20next%20to%20Bailey%20Road%2C%20is%20still%20known%20by%20his%20name.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Eshakha%20tod%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20(inter-group)%20marriages%20and%20marriages%20between%20Koeris%20and%20Dangis%20have%20started%20taking%20place%20though%20the%20rate%20is%20still%20very%20low.%20But%20it%20is%20certain%20that%20a%20period%20of%20change%20has%20begun%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Nanda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20Koeri%2C%20Kushwaha%2C%20Dangi%20or%20Kori-Kachhi%2C%20they%20are%20all%20farmers%20and%20identified%20as%20such.%20If%20ever%20they%20unify%20under%20this%20identity%2C%20Jagdev%20Prasad%E2%80%99s%20claim%20that%20%E2%80%9C90%25%20share%20in%20wealth%20land%20and%20power%20belongs%20to%20these%20castes%E2%80%9D%20might%20become%20the%20truth.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETranslated%20from%20Hindi%20by%20Naushin%20Rehman.%20Read%20the%20Hindi%20original%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22