.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20government%20said%20the%20security%20cabinet%20had%20also%20decided%20to%20deduct%20funds%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20that%20were%20designated%20for%20the%20Gaza%20Strip.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EAlthough%20Hamas%20seized%20control%20of%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fpalestinian-territories%2Ft-19099064%5C%22%3EGaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20in%202007%2C%20the%20PA%20has%20continued%20to%20pay%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20civil%20servants%20in%20the%20territory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20PA%20is%20estimated%20to%20spend%20some%2030%25%20of%20its%20budget%20in%20Gaza%2C%20where%20it%20also%20provides%20funds%20for%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%20medicine%20and%20social%20assistance%20programs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIsraeli%20forces%20complete%20%E2%80%98encirclement%20of%20Gaza%20City%2C%E2%80%99%20IDF%20says%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20military%20says%20its%20troops%20have%20pushed%20further%20into%20northern%20Gaza%20and%20%E2%80%9Ccompleted%20the%20encirclement%20of%20Gaza%20City.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20spokesperson%20Daniel%20Hagari%20added%20that%20the%20army%20had%20destroyed%20Hamas%20military%20installations%20and%20infrastructure%20as%20it%20advanced%20on%20Gaza%20City%20from%20several%20directions.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20city%20has%20become%20the%20focus%20of%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20campaign%20to%20stamp%20out%20the%20Hamas%20militant%20Islamist%20group%2C%20which%20rules%20Gaza.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%E2%80%99s%20estimated%20that%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20civilians%20remain%20in%20the%20north%20of%20the%20besieged%20territory.%20Israel%20has%20repeatedly%20claimed%20that%20Hamas%20forces%20and%20military%20assets%20are%20embedded%20in%20civilian%20infrastructure.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHagari%20stressed%20that%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fisrael-at-war%2Ft-57547294%5C%22%3EIsrael%E2%80%99s%20war%20was%20solely%20against%20the%20militants.%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CI%20want%20to%20make%20something%20very%20clear%2C%E2%80%9D%C2%A0he%C2%A0said.%20%E2%80%9CIsrael%20is%20at%20war%20with%20Hamas.%20Israel%20is%20not%20at%20war%20with%20the%20civilians%20in%20Gaza.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EHamas%20carried%20out%20terror%20attacks%20against%20Israeli%20communities%20on%20October%207%2C%20killing%201%2C400%20people%20and%20taking%20more%20than%20230%20hostages.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%20has%20since%20carried%20out%20airstrikes%20and%20expanded%20its%20ground%20operations%20in%20Gaza.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20Hamas-run%20Health%20Ministry%20said%20the%20death%20toll%20in%20the%20enclave%20had%20passed%209%2C000.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20UN%20has%20warned%20of%20a%20looming%20humanitarian%20catastrophe%20in%20Gaza%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fcease-fire-truce-armistice-whats-the-difference%2Fa-67243219%5C%22%3Ecalled%20for%20a%20cease-fire%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20allow%20aid%20to%20reach%20civilians.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIsrael%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20EU%2C%20the%20US%2C%20and%20others%2C%20have%20designated%20Hamas%20a%20terrorist%20organization.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBlinken%20to%20urge%20humanitarian%20%E2%80%98pauses%E2%80%99%20during%20Israel%20talks%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EUS%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Antony%20Blinken%20says%20his%20talks%2