20again%20is%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3Enow%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%E2%80%9D%20Only%20those%20for%20whom%20Israel%20can%20do%20no%20wrong%20will%20fail%20to%20recognise%20what%20Netanyahu%20had%20actually%20declared.%20This%20was%20that%20the%20ethnic%20cleansing%20of%20Gaza%20had%20begun.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ENetanyahu%20did%20not%20say%20anything%20that%20would%20amount%20to%20an%20admission%20that%20this%20was%20his%20goal.%20What%20he%20claimed%2C%20repeatedly%2C%20was%20that%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20purpose%20was%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20complete%20destruction%20of%20Hamas%E2%80%9D.%20But%20he%20knows%20perfectly%20well%20that%20apart%20from%20the%20few%20Hamas%20leaders%20whom%20they%20can%20currently%20identify%2C%20the%20Israeli%20Defence%20Forces%20(IDF)%20will%20never%20be%20able%20to%20tell%20who%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20group%20and%20who%20among%20Gaza%E2%80%99s%20half%20to%20three-quarters%20of%20a%20million%20adult%20males%20and%20females%20are%20Hamas%20fighters%20and%20who%20are%20not.%20So%20the%20IDF%20will%20have%20no%20alternative%20but%20to%20keep%20bombing%20known%20and%20suspected%20hide-outs%20and%20tunnels%20in%20the%20hope%20of%20flushing%20out%20Hamas%20guerillas.%20For%2C%20as%20more%20than%20one%20army%20has%20learned%20to%20its%20cost%20during%20the%20last%20century%2C%20the%20casualties%20that%20an%20attacking%20force%20sustains%20in%20the%20alternative%2C%20of%20street%20to%20street%20fighting%2C%20are%20far%20greater%20than%20those%20sustained%20by%20the%20defendants.%20The%20only%20%E2%80%98economical%E2%80%99%20way%20to%20regain%20control%20of%20a%20city%20therefore%2C%20is%20to%20pull%20it%20down%20on%20the%20defenders%E2%80%99%20heads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20leaders%20of%20Hamas%20must%20have%20been%20fully%20aware%20of%20how%20Israel%20would%20react%20even%20while%20they%20were%20planning%20their%20attack%20on%20the%20Israeli%20settlements%2C%20for%20the%20current%20Israeli%20bombing%20is%20the%20fifth%20they%20have%20faced%20in%20Gaza%20in%20the%20last%20two%20decades%2C%20with%20one%20of%20these%C2%A0%20having%20lasted%2051%20days.%20So%20they%20know%20that%20the%20safest%20place%20in%20which%20to%20hide%20their%20fighters%20is%20in%20the%20crowds%20of%20refugees%20that%20the%20bombing%2C%20and%20subsequent%20Israeli%20ground%20attack%2C%20will%20create.%20Netanyahu%20knows%20this%20too%2C%20so%20he%20knows%20that%20the%20only%20sure%20way%20to%20%E2%80%98destroy%E2%80%99%20Hamas%20is%20to%20push%20the%20entire%20population%20of%20Gaza%20into%20either%20the%20Sinai%20desert%2C%20i.e%20Egypt%2C%20or%20transfer%20it%20forcibly%20from%20Gaza%20into%20tented%20camps%20in%20the%20Negev%20desert%20.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EEither%20of%20these%20courses%20of%20action%20will%20make%20Israel%20a%20war%20criminal%20in%20international%20law.%20But%20as%C2%A0%20the%20latest%20Israeli%20assault%20on%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fgaza-internet-out-again-after-israeli-air-strikes-on-jabalia-refugee-camp%5C%22%3Erefugee%20camp%20in%20North%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%20shows%2C%20this%20has%20not%20deterred%20Netanyahu%2C%20because%20of%20his%20conviction%20that%20the%20US%20will%20continue%20to%20support%20Israel%20irrespective%20of%20what%20he%20decides.%20What%20he%20may%20have%20underestimated%2C%20however%2C%20is%20the%20degree%20of%20opposition%20that%20exists%20among%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EJewish%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%20population.%20This%20has%20been%20reflected%20by%20an%20explosive%20revelation%20in%20%E2%80%98%2B972%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20liberal%20Israeli%20magazine%2C%20that%20%E2%80%98The%20Intelligence%20Ministry%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20think%20tank%20within%20the%20Israeli%20defence%20establishment%2C%20had%20unequivocally%C2%A0%20recommended%20the%20total%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.972mag.com%2Fintelligence-ministry-gaza-population-transfer%2F%5C%22%3Ereoccupation%20of%20Gaza%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20ejection%20of%20Palestinian%20civilians%20into%20Egypt%20or%20the%20Negev%20desert%20as%20early%20as%20October%2013%2C%20six%20days%20after%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.timesofisrael.com%2Fliveblog_entry%2Fnetanyahu-brandishes-map-of-israel-that-includes-west-bank-and-gaza-at-un-speech%2F%5C%22%3Emap%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20an%20%E2%80%98Arab-free%E2%80%99%20Israel%20that%20Netanyahu%20displayed%20at%20the%20UN%20General%20Assembly%20in%20September%20shows%20that%20he%20had%20probably%20been%20aware%20of%2C%20and%20may%20even%20have%20instigated%2C%20the%20preparation%20of%20that%20plan%20well%20before%20the%20Hamas%20attack.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20whether%20the%20US%2C%20which%20has%20so%20far%20blindly%20supported%20every%20Israeli%20action%20since%20that%20country%E2%80%99s%20inception%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20do%20so%20in%20face%20of%20the%20revelation%20that%20Netanyahu%20has%20been%20not%20merely%20contemplating%20an%20action%20that%2C%20only%20a%20century%20ago%2C%20gave%20birth%20to%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98genocide%E2%80%99%20to%20describe%20the%20Armenian%20death%20march%20out%20of%20southern%20Turkey%20into%20Syria.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20could%20change%20if%20the%20democrats%20return%20to%20power%20in%202024.%20For%2C%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20hysteria%20that%20Netanyahu%20has%20created%20in%20Israel%20over%20the%20Hamas%20attack%2C%20President%20Biden%20has%20not%20minced%20his%20words%20%2C%20and%20has%20told%20Israel%20that%20it%20needs%20to%20look%20for%20a%20two-state%20solution%20as%20a%20road%20to%20peace.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBiden%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fspeeches-remarks%2F2023%2F10%2F18%2Fremarks-by-president-biden-on-the-october-7th-terrorist-attacks-and-the-resilience-of-the-state-of-israel-and-its-people-tel-aviv-israel%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThat%2527s%2520why%252C%2520as%2520hard%2520as%2Cgreater%2520integration%2520with%2520its%2520neighbors.%5C%22%3Eexact%20words%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20his%20speech%20at%20Tel%20Aviv%20are%20worth%20quoting%3A%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThat%E2%80%99s%20why%2C%20as%20hard%20as%20it%20is%2C%20we%20must%20keep%20pursuing%20peace.%20We%20must%20keep%20pursuing%20a%20path%20so%20that%20Israel%20and%20the%20Palestinian%20people%20can%20both%20live%20safely%2C%20in%20security%2C%20in%20dignity%2C%20and%20in%20peace.%20For%20me%2C%20that%20means%20a%20two-state%20solution.%20We%20must%20keep%20working%20for%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20greater%20integration%20with%20its%20neighbours.%20These%20attacks%20have%20only%20strengthened%20my%20commitment%20and%20determination%20and%20my%20will%20to%20get%20that%20done.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20theory%20a%20two-state%20solution%20would%20be%20an%20improvement%20over%20the%20present%20Israeli%20tyranny%20over%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza.%20But%20as%20the%20maps%20below%20show%2C%20creating%20it%20would%20require%20a%20mammoth%20displacement%20of%20both%20Arabs%20and%20Israelis%20from%20their%20present%20homes%20that%20neither%20community%20is%20likely%20to%20accept.%20A%20return%20of%20Israel%20to%20the%20Green%20Line%20is%20out%20because%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20unceasing%20expansion%20into%20the%20West%20Bank%2C%20and%20the%20subsequent%20Oslo%20agreements%20have%20made%20that%20line%20history.%20Today%2C%20not%20only%20does%20the%20barrier%20that%20Israel%20built%20to%20protect%20its%20settlers%20from%20PLO%20and%20Al%20Fatah%20attacks%20not%20follow%20the%20Green%20Line%2C%20but%20at%20places%20it%20penetrates%20as%20much%20as%2018%20to%2020%20kms%20to%20the%20west%20of%20it.%20Overall%2C%20the%20Wall%20has%20allowed%20Israel%20to%20annex%2013.5%25%20of%20the%20territory%20that%20was%20west%20of%20the%20original%20Green%20Line%20after%20the%20Armistice%20was%20signed%20in%201949.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20440px)%2085vw%2C%20440px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114551%2F1949.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22440%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114551%2F1949.jpg%20440w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114551%2F1949-110x300.jpg%20110w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114551%2F1949-375x1024.jpg%20375w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683276%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EUnited%20Nations%20Palestine%20map%20showing%20Armistice%20Agreements%20between%20Israel%20%26amp%3B%20Lebanon%2C%20Syria%2C%20Jordan%20%26amp%3B%20Egypt%20.%20Photo%3A%20United%20Nations%2C%20Public%20Domain%20via%20Wikimedia%20Commons%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%201993-95%20Oslo%20accords%2C%20the%20PLO%20and%20Fatah%20accepted%20a%20further%20transfer%20of%20control%20of%20the%20bulk%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20to%20Tel%20Aviv.%20This%20divided%20the%20West%20Bank%20into%20three%20areas%2C%20%E2%80%98A%E2%80%99%2C%20%E2%80%99B%E2%80%99%2C%20and%20%E2%80%98C%E2%80%99.%20Area%20C%20was%20a%20contiguous%20territory%20occupying%2061%25%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20that%20would%20be%20controlled%20completely%20by%20Israel.%20This%20was%20by%20then%20home%20to%20400%2C000%20Jews%20and%20150%2C000%20Palestinians%2C%20the%20latter%20living%20in%20532%20residential%20enclaves%20which%20are%20in%20effect%20isolated%20villages%20with%2050-60%20families%20living%20in%20each%20of%20them.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20the%20adjoining%20map%20shows%2C%20Areas%20A%20and%20B%20occupy%2017%20and%2022%25%20of%20the%20West%20Bank%20respectively.%20These%20are%20home%20to%202.8%20million%20Palestinians%20who%20live%20in%20165%20enclaves%2C%20most%20of%20which%20are%20completely%20isolated%20from%20each%20other%20by%20the%20tortuous%20contours%20drawn%20to%20define%20Area%20C.%20Even%20in%20this%20small%20area%2C%20the%20Palestinian%20Authority%20actually%20administers%20only%20Area%20A%2C%20and%20even%20there%20has%20to%20share%20its%20security%20arrangements%20with%20Israel.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114158%2FOccupied_Palestinian_Territories.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22787%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114158%2FOccupied_Palestinian_Territories.jpg%20787w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114158%2FOccupied_Palestinian_Territories-197x300.jpg%20197w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03114158%2FOccupied_Palestinian_Territories-672x1024.jpg%20672w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683272%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EPalestinian%20territories.%20Photo%3A%20Wickey-nl%2FWikimedia%20Commons%2C%20CC%20BY-SA%203.0%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ESo%20is%20there%20any%20way%20to%20untangle%20this%20web%20in%20order%20to%20obtain%20a%20two-state%20solution%3F%20The%20short%20answer%20is%20not%20while%20Netanyahu%20remains%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister.%20Netanyahu%20is%20committed%20to%20pushing%20every%20Arab%20out%20of%20Gaza%20into%20Sinai%2C%20or%20at%20best%20the%20Negev%20desert%20in%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20far%20south.%20Till%20he%20is%20forced%20out%20of%20power%2C%20peace%20between%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20will%20remain%20a%20mirage.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20should%20a%20miracle%20occur%20and%20a%20liberal%20government%20come%20to%20power%20in%20Israel%2C%20there%20is%20one%20example%20of%20a%20multi-ethnic%2C%20multi-religious%20and%20multi-cultural%20federation%20that%20it%20could%20well%20use%20as%20a%20model%20for%20Israel%20and%20Palestine.%20This%20is%20the%20ethno-federal%20democracy%20of%20India.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20citizens%20belong%20to%20more%20than%202%2C000%20ethnic%20groups%2C%20each%20with%20its%20own%20history%2C%20language%20and%20culture%2C%20who%20speak%2022%20major%20languages%2C%20and%20innumerable%20dialects.%20Its%20constitution%20has%20harmonised%20this%20through%20a%20multi-tier%20democratic%20system%20with%20elected%20village%20councils%20making%20up%20the%20bottom%20tier%2C%20through%2028%20elected%20state%20governments%2C%20with%20a%20single%20national%20government%20at%20its%20apex.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIts%20constitution%2C%20which%20is%20by%20far%20the%20longest%20in%20the%20world%2C%20reserves%20defence%2C%20foreign%20affairs%2C%20international%20trade%20and%20finance%2C%20and%20the%20framing%20of%20criminal%20and%20civil%20law%2C%20to%20the%20Central%20government%20and%20leaves%20land%2C%20agriculture%2C%20health%2C%20education%2C%20culture%20and%20the%20administration%20of%20law%2C%20to%20the%20state%20governments.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20is%20home%20to%20eight%20major%20religions%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%93%20Jainism%2C%20Buddhism%2C%20Hinduism%2C%20Islam%2C%20Christianity%2C%20Judaism%2C%20Zoroastrianism%20and%20Sikhism%2C%20and%20their%20many%20branches.%20Its%20constitution%20protects%20not%20only%20their%20customs%20but%20also%20their%20religious%20laws.%20Within%20this%20framework%2C%20all%20of%20its%20citizens%20enjoy%20complete%20equality%20and%20the%20same%20civic%20rights%20and%20protections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%E2%80%99s%20success%20in%20forging%20a%20peaceful%20nation%20out%20of%20such%20enormous%20diversity%20without%20resorting%20to%20war%20has%20been%20so%20complete%20that%20it%20barely%20draws%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20attention%20any%20longer.%20But%20the%20construction%20of%20its%20complex%20democracy%20has%20been%20an%20ongoing%20process%2C%20that%20began%2012%20years%20before%20India%20became%20independent%2C%20in%201935%20and%20is%20still%20a%20work%20in%20progress%2C%2088%20years%20later.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%201935%20constitution%20gave%20India%20a%20federal%20structure%20that%20was%20based%20upon%20the%20British%20political%20structures%20that%20already%20existed%20at%20the%20time%20when%20they%20built%20their%20empire.%20The%201948%20constitution%2C%20followed%20by%20the%20linguistic%20reorganisation%20of%20state%20borders%20in%201957%2C%20created%20the%20federal%2C%C2%A0%20ethnicity-based%20%E2%80%98Union%20of%20States%E2%80%99%20that%20India%20is%20today.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIsrael%20and%20Palestine%20could%2C%20if%20they%20desired%2C%20merge%20to%20create%20a%20similar%20ethno-federal%20nation%2C%20with%20Jerusalem%20as%20its%20capital%2C%20and%20Israel%2C%20the%20West%20Bank%20and%20Gaza%20as%20its%20federating%20units%2C%20each%C2%A0%20with%20its%20own%20state%20capital%20and%2C%20if%20desired%2C%20its%20own%20official%20religion.%20Jerusalem%2C%20however%2C%20would%20be%20open%20to%20all%20the%20faiths%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20the%20world.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ECreating%20a%20single%2C%20federated%20nation%20will%20make%20it%20unnecessary%20to%20engineer%20any%20shift%20of%20population%20or%20exchange%20of%20territory%20within%20it.%20That%20will%20end%20the%20principal%20cause%20of%20the%20conflict%20that%20has%20bedevilled%20Palestine%20till%20today.%20Israelis%20and%20Palestinian%20Arabs%20will%20be%20able%20to%20live%20and%20work%20freely%20in%20any%20part%20of%20the%20country%2C%20and%20to%20buy%20and%20sell%20property%20freely%20if%20they%20wish%20to%20move%20elsewhere.%20This%20nation%20would%20need%20two%20official%20languages%2C%20but%20could%2C%20for%20a%20transitional%20period%20at%20least%2C%20use%20English%20as%20the%20link%20language%20between%20its%20governments%20and%20their%20subsidiary%20agencies.%20The%20greatest%20boon%20that%20it%C2%A0%20will%20confer%20upon%20both%20peoples%20is%20peace%20%E2%80%93%20the%20freedom%20to%20continue%20living%20where%20they%20live%20today%20with%20all%20the%20rights%20of%20a%20free%20people%2C%20and%20without%20fear.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20Gideon%20Levy%2C%20the%20famed%20columnist%20of%20the%20Israeli%20newspaper%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EHaaretz%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E%2C%20told%20the%20National%20Press%20Club%20at%20Washington%20in%202015%2C%20the%20two%20essential%20requirements%20of%20such%20a%20transition%20are%20mutual%20respect%20and%20a%20desire%20for%20peace.%20These%20have%20been%20noticeably%20absent%20among%20the%20Jews%20of%20Israel%20and%20the%20Arabs%20of%20West%20Bank%20because%20of%20the%20US%E2%80%99s%20unstinting%20support%20of%20every%20military%20or%20diplomatic%20initiative%20that%20Israel%20has%20taken%20regardless%20of%20its%20rights%20and%20wrongs.%20This%20blind%20support%20is%20what%20Netanyahu%20has%20capitalised%20upon%20to%20cage%20and%20progressively%20dehumanise%20Palestinian%20Arabs%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20the%20world.%20If%20Hamas%E2%80%99s%20violent%20incursion%20on%20October%207%20and%20Israel%E2%80%99s%20genocidal%20response%20in%20Gaza%20bring%20home%20the%20futility%20of%20perennial%20confrontation%2C%20then%20the%20thousands%20who%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20and%20the%20thousands%20more%20who%20will%20do%20so%20in%20the%20next%20few%20weeks%2C%20will%20not%20have%20died%20in%20vain.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Fprem-shankar-jha%5C%22%3EPrem%20Shankar%20Jha%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20veteran%20journalist.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698993641000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F03120804%2Fisrael-palestine.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-peace-india-model%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20moment%2C%20a%20two-state%20solution%20for%20Israel%20and%20Palestine%20seems%20impossible.%20But%20should%20a%20miracle%20occur%2C%20there%20is%20one%20example%20of%20a%20multi-ethnic%2C%20multi-religious%20and%20multi-cultural%20federation%20that%20could%20be%20a%20model%3A%20the%20ethno-federal%20democracy%20of%20India.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A14%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fisrael-palestine-peace-india-model%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Shalini%20Pandey%20lauds%20'Animal'%20teaser%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698993373000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-104935193%2Cimgsize-72878.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fshalini-pandey-of-arjun-reddy-fame-lauds-teaser-of-ranbir-kapoor-starrer-animal-calls-director-sandeep-reddy-vanga-impactful%2Farticleshow%2F104935193.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F104935193.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EActress%20Shalini%20Pandey%20praised%20the%20teaser%20of%20the%20upcoming%20film%20'Animal'%20directed%20by%20Sandeep%20Reddy%20Vanga.%20She%20expressed%20her%20admiration%20for%20Vanga's%20impactful%20directing%20style%20and%20revealed%20her%20strong%20bond%20with%20the%20director.%20Despite%20her%20previous%20film%20