%20Developmental%20Inclusive%20Alliance%20(INDIA)%2C%20are%20working%20to%20free%20the%20media%20too%20%E2%80%A6%20the%20media%20will%20have%20its%20freedom%20back%20when%20we%20are%20in%20power.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%20criticised%20the%20exercise.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%20and%20the%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20Dal%20(RJD)%20are%20locked%20in%20the%20battle%20to%20take%20credit.%20Over%2030%2C000%20non-Biharis%20have%20got%20jobs%20at%20the%20cost%20of%20Bihar%E2%80%99s%20youths%E2%80%9D%2C%20senior%20BJP%20leader%20Sushil%20Kumar%20Modi%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EOther%20saffron%20leaders%20alleged%20%E2%80%9Cirregularities%E2%80%9D%20in%20the%20exercise.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ETejashwi%20Yadav%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhat%20will%20the%20BJP%20say%3F%20The%20PM%20has%20miserably%20failed%20on%20his%20promise%20of%20giving%20jobs.%20They%20%5Bthe%20BJP%5D%20are%20not%20talking%20about%20their%20leader%E2%80%99s%20%3Ci%3Ejumlabaji%3C%2Fi%3E%20(false%20promises)%20and%20inability%20to%20deliver%20goods.%20They%20stand%20exposed.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20exercise%20to%20give%20appointment%20letters%20involved%20participation%20of%20the%20Bihar%20Public%20Service%20Commission%20(BPSC)%20and%20the%20education%20department%20and%20took%20six%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20293px)%2085vw%2C%20293px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02185142%2FK.-K.-Pathak-293x300.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22293%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02185142%2FK.-K.-Pathak-293x300.jpg%20293w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02185142%2FK.-K.-Pathak.jpg%20571w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683217%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22300%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EAdditional%20chief%20secretary%20of%20the%20education%20department%2C%20K.K.%20Pathak%20(IAS).%20Photo%3A%20Special%20arrangement.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EAdditional%20secretary%20of%20the%20education%20department%20and%20professor%20K.K.%20Pathak%20(IAS)%20was%20also%20involved%20in%20the%20preparations%20for%20the%20job%20event.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBackground%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFrom%202007%20to%202020%2C%20Nitish%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20learned%20to%20have%20given%20appointment%20letters%20to%20five%20lakh%20youths%2C%20mostly%20as%20teachers%2C%20but%20it%20never%20in%20one%20go%20and%20reflected%20many%20discrepancies%20at%20various%20stages.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20BPSC%20%E2%80%93%20that%20employs%20deputy%20collector-level%20officers%20%E2%80%93%20has%20recruited%20teachersm%20adopting%20rigorous%20competitive%20exams.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20background%20of%20what%20the%20common%20people%20describe%20as%20the%20job%20%3Ci%3Emahakumbha%3C%2Fi%3E%20in%20the%20state%20is%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%E2%80%99s%20promise%20during%20the%202020%20assembly%20elections%20that%20he%20would%20give%2010%20lakh%20jobs%20to%20the%20youth%20if%20his%20party%20came%20to%20power.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHis%20RJD%20was%20in%20the%20opposition%20then%20against%20the%20JDU-BJP%20combine.%20The%20RJD%20emerged%20as%20the%20single%20largest%20party%20in%202020.%20It%20failed%20to%20replace%20the%20JDU-BJP%20combine%20by%20a%20whisker.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EBut%20his%20promise%20of%20employment%20was%20believed%20to%20have%20helped%20Tejashwi%20emerge%20as%20the%20leader%20of%20the%20youth%20in%20his%20own%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20joined%20the%20Nitish-led%20%3Cem%3Emahagathbandhan%3C%2Fem%3E%20government%20in%20August%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EInspiration%20from%20Karpoori%20Thakur%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20219px)%2085vw%2C%20219px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%