AYxZl-242x300.jpeg%20242w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-683250%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22493%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20placard%20among%20protesters%20at%20IIT-BHU.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40CareerWtPrakhar%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20students%20demanded%20better%20security%20arrangement%2C%20including%20a%20closed%20campus%2C%20opposition%20parties%20targeted%20the%20BJP%20government%20for%20the%20poor%20law%20and%20order%2C%20with%20Congress%20leader%20Priyanka%20Gandhi%20Vadra%20wondering%2C%20in%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20%E2%80%9Cno%20longer%20possible%E2%80%9D%20for%20a%20female%20student%20in%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%20Varanasi%20%E2%80%9Cto%20walk%20fearlessly%20inside%20her%20own%20educational%20institution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAmbushed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%2C%20according%20to%20the%20student%E2%80%99s%20complaint%2C%20happened%20when%20she%2C%20along%20with%20a%20male%20friend%2C%20had%20stepped%20out%20for%20a%20walk%20near%20her%20hostel%20at%20around%201%3A30%20am%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20student%20said%20that%20around%20300-400%20nears%20the%20Karman%20Baba%20temple%20in%20the%20campus%2C%20a%20bike%20carrying%20three%20people%20ambushed%20her%20and%20her%20male%20friend%20from%20behind.%20The%20men%20separated%20the%20two%20and%20dragged%20the%20girl%20to%20a%20corner%20while%20covering%20her%20mouth%2C%20she%20alleged.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20miscreants%20then%20forcibly%20kissed%20her%2C%20disrobed%20her%20and%20clicked%20videos%20and%20photos%20of%20her%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20screamed%20for%20help%2C%20they%20threatened%20to%20kill%20me%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20student%20said%20in%20her%20police%20complaint.%20The%20men%20held%20her%20for%2010-15%20minutes%20and%20secured%20her%20phone%20number%20before%20letting%20her%20go.%20The%20student%20hid%20in%20a%20professor%E2%80%99s%20residence%C2%A0nearby%C2%A0fearing%20a%20repeat%20of%20the%20attack.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20was%20lodged%20against%20three%20unidentified%20persons%20under%20assault%20or%20use%20of%20criminal%20force%20to%20woman%20with%20intent%20to%20disrobe%2C%20criminal%20intimidation%20and%20relevant%20sections%20of%20the%20Information%20Technology%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Not%20the%20first%20time%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IIT%20BHU%20Students%E2%80%99%20Parliament%2C%20a%20body%20of%20the%20students%20on%20campus%2C%20said%20the%20%E2%80%9Cheinous%20crime%E2%80%9D%20had%20shaken%20the%20%E2%80%9Cvery%20fibre%20of%20the%20institution.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20also%20not%20the%20first%20time%20such%20an%20incident%20has%20occurred%20on%20campus.%20Students%20have%20repeatedly%20raised%20concerns%20about%20security%20on%20campus%2C%20but%20the%20administration%20has%20failed%20to%20take%20adequate%20action%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20student%20body%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IIT%20BHU%20students%20staged%20a%20huge%20protest%20against%20the%20incident%20and%20demanded%20that%20the%20administration%20carry%20out%20night%20barricading%20to%20restrict%20entry%20of%20outside%20vehicles%20inside%20the%20campus%20with%20a%20single%20point%20of%20entry%20and%20exit%2C%20set%20up%20a%20centralised%20CCTV%20system%2C%20escalate%20legal%20action%20against%20violent%20offenders%2C%20increase%20CCTV%20infrastructure%20and%20take%20immediate%20on-ground%20and%20legal%20action%20on%20such%20incidents.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20protest%20went%20on%20till%20late%20on%20Thursday%2C%20forcing%20officials%20to%20take%20action%20and%20issue%20assurances%20to%20the%20agitated%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIndeed%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20students%20in%20BHU%20have%20staged%20a%20protest%20against%20an%20unsafe%20campus%20for%20girls%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202017%2C%20BHU%20students%20staged%20a%20dharna%20in%20the%20campus%20against%20the%20alleged%20victim-blaming%20of%20a%20female%20student%20who%20was%20molested%20by%20two%20unknown%20persons%20while%20she%20was%20returning%20to%20her%20hostel.%20Even%20though%20there%20were%20security%20guards%20stationed%20at%20a%20distance%2C%20the%20fine%20arts%20student%20did%20not%20receive%20any%20help%20and%20was%20instead%20snubbed%20with%20misogynist%20remarks%20and%20shamed%20for%20walking%20in%20the%20dark.%20The%202017%20protest%20came%20under%20focus%20after%20the%20police%20carried%20out%20a%20lathi-charge%20on%20the%20protesting%20students.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20February%20this%20year%2C%20students%20staged%20a%20protest%20after%20a%20differently-abled%20student%20was%20allegedly%20molested%20by%20a%20youth%2C%20the%20son%20of%20a%20BHU%20academician%2C%20on%20the%20pretext%20of%20offering%20her%20a%20lift.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Admin%20attitude%20puts%20blame%20on%20girls%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%202022%2C%20the%20Bhagat%20Singh%20Students%20Morcha%20even%20submitted%20a%20memorandum%20to%20the%20chief%20proctors%20highlighting%20the%20unsafe%20conditions%20in%20the%20campus%2C%20which%20is%20not%20only%20poorly-lit%20but%20also%20porous%20and%20accessible%20to%20outsiders%20as%20it%20is%20in%20the%20midst%20of%20dense%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20IIT-BHU%20incident%20was%20not%20an%20isolated%20one.%20Every%20other%20month%20we%20come%20across%20such%20cases%20of%20sexual%20harassment.%20Most%20girls%20don%E2%80%99t%20even%20report%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ipsita%2C%20a%20student%20associated%20with%20the%20BSSM%2C%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20the%20administration%20lacked%20sensitivity%20towards%20the%20issue.%20%E2%80%9CTheir%20attitude%20is%20always%20that%20it%20is%20the%20girls%20who%20are%20at%20fault%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Committee%20to%20submit%20report%E2%80%99%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ELater%20on%20Thursday%2C%20IIT%20BHU%20administration%20informed%20the%20protesting%20students%20that%20the%20Commissioner%20of%20Varanasi%20had%20apprised%20them%20that%20he%20had%20discussed%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20about%20construction%20of%20a%20boundary%20wall%20of%20the%20institute%20campus.%20A%20joint%20committee%20of%20CPWD%20officials%20and%20an%20IIT-BHU%20professor%20will%20be%20constituted%20and%20entrusted%20with%20the%20task%20of%20surveying%20the%20campus%20for%20construction%20of%20a%20boundary%20wall%20to%20augment%20its%20safety%2C%20the%20IIT-BHU%20Registrar%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20committee%20will%20submit%20its%20report%20within%20a%20week.%20The%20Varanasi%20Commissioner%20also%20said%20that%20CCTV%20cameras%20would%20be%20installed%20at%20all%20sensitive%20locations%20including%20girls%E2%80%99%20hostels%20at%20the%20earliest.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20IIT-BHU%20administration%20also%20decided%20to%20restrict%20movement%20of%20vehicles%20within%20the%20campus%20from%2010%20pm%20to%205%20am%20by%20putting%20barricades%20at%20specified%20locations%20and%20deploying%20additional%20security%20at%20sensitive%20places.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20security%20of%20the%20institute%20would%20be%20jointly%20monitored%20by%20the%20district%20police%20and%20IIT-BHU%20personnels%20at%20all%20the%20seven%20gates%2C%20while%20four%20police%20personnel%20including%20a%20sub-inspector%20would%20be%20permanently%20positioned%20in%20the%20chief%20proctor%20office%20of%20the%20institute%20to%20take%20necessary%20action.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20institute%20also%20said%20it%20would%20actively%20pursue%20with%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Education%20and%20the%20university%20administration%20for%20creation%20of%20a%20closed%20campus%20with%20restricted%20entry.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698981297000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fw