ittle%20or%20no%20regulation%20or%20legislation%20to%20contain%20AI%2C%20and%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20international%20agreement%20to%20deal%20with%20an%20emerging%20phenomenon%20that%20crosses%20borders%20instantly%20and%20silently.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20week%2C%20British%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20is%20hosting%20an%20international%20gathering%20intended%20to%20kick-start%20international%20discussion%20about%20the%20benefits%20and%20perils%20of%20AI%2C%20and%20how%20one%20is%20maximised%20and%20the%20other%20kept%20at%20bay.%20The%20venue%20is%20Bletchley%20Park%20in%20southern%20England%2C%20once%20the%20base%20of%20Britain%E2%80%99s%20Second%20World%20War%20codebreakers%20so%20crucial%20to%20achieving%20victory%20over%20Nazi%20Germany.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20so%20often%2C%20the%20summit%20also%20has%20a%20political%20purpose.%20Sunak%E2%80%99s%20government%20is%20drifting%2C%20and%20his%20personal%20popularity%20is%20plummeting%20with%20an%20election%20probably%20about%20a%20year%20away.%20This%20is%20one%20way%20that%20the%20UK%E2%80%99s%20prime%20minister%20can%20suggest%20he%E2%80%99s%20a%20man%20of%20action%2C%20a%20leader%20for%20the%20digital%20era%2C%20seeking%20to%20spearhead%20a%20global%20response%20to%20an%20emerging%20issue.%20And%20he%20wants%20to%20position%20Britain%20as%20an%20AI%20superpower%2C%20a%20hub%20of%20technological%20excellence%20and%20best%20practice.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Artificial%20Intelligence%20Safety%20Summit%2C%20to%20give%20the%20gathering%20its%20formal%20title%2C%20is%20intended%20to%20identify%20the%20risks%20posed%20by%20the%20rapid%20development%20of%20superintelligent%20technaisologies.%20The%20potential%20advantages%20are%20huge%3A%20speedy%20and%20reliable%20medical%20diagnosis%2C%20and%20perhaps%20treatment%3B%20the%20opportunity%20to%20phase%20out%20humdrum%20administrative%20work%3B%20and%20the%20advent%20of%20a%20new%20era%20of%20