tiful%20force%20for%20good%2C%20had%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20so%20evil.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEllison%20testified%3A%20%26quot%3BSam%20directed%20me%20to%20commit%20these%20crimes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Caroline%20Ellison%2C%20SBF%20trial%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6526e5aa68f1d46f52aeef77%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221969%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECaroline%20Ellison%20testified%20for%20two%20days%20at%20the%20criminal%20trial%20of%20SBF.%3Cp%3EEduardo%20Munoz%20Alvarez%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20defense%20tried%20to%20paint%20a%20different%20picture.%20Ellison%2C%20Wang%2C%20and%20Singh%20%E2%80%94%20along%20with%20the%20prosecutors%20in%20the%20case%20%E2%80%94%20cast%20Bankman-Fried%20as%20a%20monstrous%20villain%2C%20defense%20attorney%20Mark%20Cohen%20said.%20He%20added%20that%20the%20trio%20of%20co-conspirators%20had%20their%20own%20culpability%2C%20repeatedly%20reminding%20the%20jury%20that%20they%20secured%20cooperation%20agreements%20with%20the%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20wrote%20him%20into%20this%20movie%20as%20a%20villain%2C%20a%20bad%20guy%2C%20directing%20others%2C%20who%20apparently%20had%20no%20free%20will%20of%20their%20own%2C%20to%20steal%20billions%20of%20dollars%2C%26quot%3B%20Cohen%20said%20of%20Bankman-Fried%20during%20closing%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20depiction%20of%20him%20made%20no%20sense%20in%20the%20real%20world%2C%20especially%20coming%20from%20these%20witnesses%20who%20were%20his%20closest%20friends%2C%20who%20knew%20him%20for%20years%2C%20who%20had%20gone%20to%20camp%20with%20him%2C%20to%20college%2C%20who%20had%20lived%20together%20with%20him%2C%20who'd%20worked%20with%20him%20for%20years%2C%20starting%20two%20businesses%2C%20who%20traveled%20with%20him%20and%20moved%20all%20over%20the%20world%20with%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BThat's