that%20much%20more%20damning%20and%20set%20the%20stage%20for%20it%20to%20boomerang%20back%20to%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20knew%20Wang%20and%20Yedidia%20from%20MIT%3B%20Singh%20was%20a%20family%20friend%3B%20Ellison%20was%20his%20on-again-off-again%20girlfriend%20he%20met%20at%20his%20first%20job%20out%20of%20college.%20They%20testified%20to%20respecting%20Bankman-Fried%20and%20trusting%20his%20judgment.%20When%20they%20thought%20his%20instructions%20were%20questionable%20(or%20unethical%2C%20or%20illegal)%2C%20they%20may%20have%20pushed%20back%2C%20but%20said%20they%20ultimately%20placed%20their%20faith%20in%20his%20seemingly%20reasonable%20explanations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SBF%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F653aabc40487ff031caf9467%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22900%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEllison%2C%20Bankman-Fried%2C%20Singh%2C%20and%20Wang.%20%3Cp%3EChelsea%20Jia%20Feng%2FInsider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20Wang%2C%20Ellison%2C%20and%20Singh%20have%20pleaded%20guilty%20to%20felonies%20and%20are%20awaiting%20their%20sentences%20after%20they%20cooperated%20in%20this%20trial.%20While%20Bankman-Fried%20faces%20over%20a%20century%20in%20prison%2C%20the%20co-conspirators%20could%20potentially%20dodge%20prison%20time%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELead%20prosecutor%20Danielle%20Sassoon%20said%20that%20Bankman-Fried%20thought%20he%20could%20%26quot%3Bget%20away%20with%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BHe%20didn't%20bargain%20for%20his%20three%20loyal%20deputies%20taking%20that%20stand%20and%20telling%20you%20the%20truth%2C%20that%20he%20was%20the%20one%20with%20the%20plan%2C%20the%20motive%2C%20and%20the%20greed%20to%20raid%20FTX%20customer%20deposits%2C%20billions%20and%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20give%20himself%20money%2C%20power%2C%20influence%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20in%20her%20closing%20argument.%20%26quot%3BHe%20thought%20the%20rules%20did%20not%20apply%20to%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBankman-Fried%20tried%20to%20flip%20the%20script%20but%20couldn't%20'recall'%20key%20details%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20hearing%20his%20ex-friends%20testify%2C%20Bankman-Fried%20made%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-ftx-testifies-criminal-fraud-trial-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erisky%20move%20to%20take%20the%20stand%20himself%20%3C%2Fa%3Eto%20tell%20his%20version%20of%20the%20story.%20He%20was%20polished%20when%20questioned%20by%20his%20own%20attorney%2C%20saying%20he%20should've%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-testifies-regrets-not-risk-management-team-ftx-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprioritized%20risk%20management%20more%3C%2Fa%3E%20than%20he%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20became%20a%20%26quot%3Bdifferent%20person%26quot%3B%20on%20cross-examination%20and%20%26quot%3Bcouldn't%20remember%20a%20single%20detail%20about%20his%20company%20or%20what%20he%20said%20publicly%2C%26quot%3B%20Assistant%20US%20Attorney%20Roos%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBankman-Fried%20claimed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-bankman-fried-repeatedly-jury-remember-words-actions-ceo-ftx-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehe%20couldn't%20recall%20details%3C%2Fa%3E%20over%20140%20times%2C%20the%20prosecutor%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20jury%20likely%20saw%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethrough%20Bankman-Fried's%20claims%20of%20ignorance%20and%20selective%20amnesia%2C%20Angel%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20somebody%20does%20the%20'I%20cannot%20recall'%20over%20and%20over%20again%2C%20it%20sure%20sounds%20fishy%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPerhaps%20Bankman-Fried%20%26quot%3Bgot%20in%20over%20his%20head%26quot%3B%20with%20the%20fraud%20scheme%2C%20but%20it%20doesn