20defense.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20issues%20with%20the%20person%20who%20is%20also%20sitting%20on%20the%20bench%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20do%20feel%2C%20like%20Mr.%20Kise%2C%20that%20your%20position%20is%20often%20what%20you're%20given%20in%20notes.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20heated%20exchange%20was%20tangential%20to%20a%20weightier%20effort%20by%20the%20attorney%20general's%20office.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEric%20Trump%20had%20spent%20the%20afternoon%20defending%20his%20sometimes%20faulty%20memory%20under%20direct%20examination%20by%20Amer%2C%20who%20is%20a%20special%20counsel%20to%20state%20Attorney%20General%20Letitia%20James.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHoning%20to%20what%20he'd%20testified%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-trial-ag-shows-previously-unseen-deposition-that-showed-family-deny-fraud-2023-10%5C%22%3Ein%20an%20earlier%20deposition%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Eric%20Trump%20repeated%20on%20the%20witness%20stand%20Thursday%20that%20he%20was%20never%20involved%20in%20drafting%20the%20decade%20of%20annual%20net-worth%20statements%20that%20his%20father%20used%20to%20secure%20more%20than%20%24400%20million%20in%20bank%20loans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AG%20says%20these%20statements%20contained%20as%20much%20as%20%243.6%20billion%20in%20intentional%20exaggerations%20each%20year%3B%20they%20are%20at%20the%20center%20of%20the%20ongoing%20trial.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20Thursday%2C%20Amer%20showed%20Eric%20Trump%20decade-old%20emails%20that%20appeared%20to%20contradict%20his%20claim%20that%20he%20was%20never%20involved%20in%20preparing%20the%20statements.%20He%20dug%20in%20under%20questioning.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20a%20major%20organization%2C%26quot%3B%20Eric%20Trump%20told%20the%20AG's%20lawyer.%20%26quot%3BA%20massive%20real-estate%20organization.%20Yes%2C%20I'm%20fairly%20sure%20I%20understand%20we%20have%20financial%20statements.%20But%20I%20had%20no%20involvement%20and%20never%20worked%20on%20my%20father's%20statement%20of%20financial%20condition%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20using%20the%20formal%20name%20for%20the%20annual%20net-worth%20statements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20on%20a%20thousand%20calls%20a%20day%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20former%20president's%20second-oldest%20son%20later%20protested%2C%20when%20Amer%20confronted%20him%20with%20evidence%20of%20a%202021%20video%20call%20where%20that%20year's%20net-worth%20statement%20was%20discussed.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%20Thursday%2C%20the%20judge%20did%20not%20expand%20the%20gag%20order.%20But%20before%20calling%20an%20end%20to%20testimony%20for%20the%20day%2C%20and%20instructing%20Eric%20Trump%20to%20return%20Friday%20morning%2C%20he%20had%20the%20final%20word%20%E2%80%93%20or%20rather%2C%20the%20final%20long%20paragraph.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMr.%20Kise%20and%20the%20rest%20of%20your%20team%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judge%20said%2C%20addressing%20the%20defense%20table.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20an%20absolute%20right%2C%20an%20absolute%20unfettered%20right%2C%20to%20get%20advice%20from%20my%20principal%20law%20clerk%2C%26quot%3B%20as%20with%20anyone%20on%20his%20three-member%20staff%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20no%20First%20Amendment%20value%20that%20I%20can%20see%20to%20referring%20to%20her%2C%20particularly%20when%20making%20things%20up%20%E2%80%93%20and%20that's%20not%20you%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Kise.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat's%20somebody%20else%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20likely%20referring%20to%20Trump%2C%20who's%20been%20in%20hot%20water%20from%20the%20judge%20twice%20for%20a%20Truth%20Social%20post%20that%20falsely%20said%20the%20clerk%20is%20the%20girlfriend%20of%20Senate%20Majority%20Leader%20Chuck%20Schumer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKise%20said%20he's%20weighed%20the%20lawyer's%20first%20amendment%20rights%20against%20the%20safety%20of%20his%20staff%2C%20and%20his%20%26quot%3Bpoints%20are%20not%20well%20taken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm