rank-call-by-russian-comedians-12998945%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Famp%2Fitalys-pm-giorgia-meloni-talks-of-ukraine-war-fatigue-after-falling-victim-to-prank-call-by-russian-comedians-12998945%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Developing%20Countries%20Are%20Underfinanced%2C%20Underprepared%20to%20Adapt%20to%20Climate%20Change%3A%20UNEP%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02214750%2Fimage-1468.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EKochi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20Developing%20countries%20are%20underfinanced%20and%20underprepared%20to%20adapt%20to%20the%20impacts%20that%20climate%20change%20is%20causing%2C%20said%20the%20United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme%E2%80%99s%20(UNEP)%20Adaptation%20Gap%20Report%2C%20released%20on%20November%202.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20provides%20an%20update%20on%20the%20global%20status%20and%20progress%20of%20adaptation%20measures%20aimed%20at%20addressing%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20with%20a%20specific%20focus%20on%20adaptation%20planning%2C%20financing%2C%20and%20implementation.%20It%20also%20highlights%20regions%20of%20urgent%20action.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20found%20that%20the%20adaptation%20finance%20gap%20is%20widening%20and%20now%20stands%20at%20between%20%24194%20billion%20and%20%24366%20billion%20per%20year.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdaptation%20finance%20needs%20are%2010%20to%2018%20times%20as%20high%20as%20the%20current%20international%20public%20adaptation%20finance%2C%20which%20is%20at%20least%2050%25%20higher%20than%20the%20estimates%20released%20by%20the%20UNEP%20last%20year%20in%20a%20similar%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20developing%20countries%20are%20ready%20and%20waiting%20to%20receive%20adaptation%20funds%2C%20experts%20and%20activists%20ask%20where%20it%20is%2C%20as%20they%20highlight%20the%20dire%20need%20for%20adaptation%20finance.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EAdapting%20to%20climate%20change%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIndia%20and%20other%20developing%20countries%20%E2%80%93%20many%20in%20the%20tropics%20%E2%80%93%20often%20bear%20the%20brunt%20of%20the%20impacts%20of%20climate%20change%2C%20ranging%20from%20scorching%20heatwaves%20to%20intense%20bouts%20of%20sudden%20rainfall.%20As%20the%20impacts%20become%20more%20frequent%20and%20intense%2C%20it%20is%20important%20that%20people%20are%20given%20the%20knowledge%2C%20means%20and%20money%20to%20adapt%20to%20these%20changes.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20climate%20change%20adaptation%20measures%20deal%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20UNEP%20defines%20adaptation%20as%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20process%20of%20adjustment%20to%20actual%20or%20expected%20climate%20and%20its%20effects.%E2%80%9D%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAdaptation%20measures%20vary%20widely%20and%20are%20often%20context-specific.%20Setting%20up%20early%20warning%20systems%20to%20predict%20extreme%20weather%20events%20such%20as%20cyclones%20so%20that%20people%20can%20prepare%20for%20the%20storm%20is%20one%20example.%20Another%20is%20switching%20to%20drought-resistant%20crops%2C%20or%20investing%20in%20proper%20rain-water%20harvesting%20systems%20to%20tackle%20water%20shortages%20and%20groundwater%20depletion%20that%20are%20already%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sciencedirect.com%2Fscience%2Farticle%2Fabs%2Fpii%2FS0022169421001505%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Eoccurring%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20in%20many%20parts%20of%20India.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThese%20adaptations%20require%20money%2C%20and%20developed%20nations%20have%20pledged%20to%20fund%20adaptation%20measures%20in%20developing%20countries%2C%20such%20as%20through%20the%20Global%20Adaptation%20Fund.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20there%20are%20gaps%20in%20funding.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fleaning-into-indigenous-knowledge-on-climate-change%2F%5C%22%3ELeaning%20Into%20Indigenous%20Knowledge%20on%20Climate%20Change%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELast%20year%E2%80%99s%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.unep.org%2Fevents%2Fpublication-launch%2Fadaptation-gap-report-2022%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EAdaptation%20Gap%20Report%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20didn%E2%80%99t%20carry%20good%20news.%20Though%20the%20world%20is%20progressing%20in%20adapting%20to%20climate%20change%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20just%20not%20enough%20to%20tackle%20the%20kind%20of%20climate%20impacts%20we%E2%80%99re%20witnessing%2C%20it%20said.%20It%20found%20that%20international%20adaptation%20finance%20flows%20to%20developing%20countries%20were%20five%20to%20ten%20times%20below%20estimated%20needs.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20year%E2%80%99s%20report%20brings%20worse%20news%3A%20the%20adaptation%20gap%20is%20widening%2C%20and%20drastically.%20The%20gap%20in%20adaptation%20finance%20now%20ranges%20between%20%24194%20to%20%24366%20billion%20per%20year%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20This%20is%2010%20to%2018%20times%20as%20high%20as%20the%20current%20international%20public%20adaptation%20finance%20flows%2C%20and%20per%20the%20report%2C%20over%2050%25%20higher%20than%20the%20previous%20estimated%20range.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDeveloping%20countries%20now%20also%20need%20higher%20funds%20for%20adaptation%3A%20the%20report%20estimates%20it%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9Cin%20a%20plausible%20central%20range%E2%80%9D%20of%20%24215%20to%20%24387%20billion%20per%20year%20this%20decade.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFurther%2C%20adaptation%20funds%20have%20slowed%20down%20since%202020%2C%20and%20adaptation%20planning%20and%20implementation%20are%20plateauing%20too%2C%20per%20the%20report.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CGender%20equality%20and%20social%20inclusion%20are%20inadequately%20included%20in%20adaptation%20finance%20needs%20and%20flows%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20report%20also%20noted.%20%E2%80%9CBridging%20the%20adaptation%20finance%20gap%20requires%20more%20international%2C%20domestic%20and%20private%20finance%2C%20ideally%20a%20reform%20of%20the%20global%20financial%20architecture%20and%20better%20international%20cooperation%2C%E2%80%9D%20it%20read.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EUN%20Secretary-General%20Ant%C3%B3nio%20Guterres%2C%20in%20his%20message%20on%20the%20report%2C%20said%20that%20we%20are%20in%20an%20%E2%80%9Cadaptation%20emergency%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20must%20act%20like%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Guterres%20said.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20take%20steps%20to%20close%20the%20adaptation%20gap%2C%20now.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20report%20has%20been%20released%20within%20less%20than%20a%20month%20of%20the%2028th%20Conference%20of%20Parties%20(COP28)%2C%20the%20UN%E2%80%99s%20climate%20change%20conference%20that%20is%20scheduled%20to%20take%20place%20in%20Dubai%2C%20United%20Arab%20Emirates.%20World%20leaders%20and%20government%20representatives%20will%20discuss%20and%20engage%20on%20crucial%20aspects%20of%20climate%20change%20at%20COP28%2C%20and%20adaptation%20funding%20is%20also%20one%20of%20the%20many%20on%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EActivists%20and%20experts%20have%20highlighted%20the%20dire%20status%20of%20adaptation%20funding%20for%20developing%20countries.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20widening%20gap%20in%20adaptation%20finance%20is%20a%20stark%20indicator%20of%20years%20of%20neglect%2C%20leaving%20countless%20vulnerable%20people%20exposed%20to%20escalating%20climate%20calamities%2C%E2%80%9D%20Harjeet%20Singh%2C%20head%20of%20global%20political%20strategy%20at%20Climate%20Action%20Network%20International%2C%20told%20Climate%20Trends%2C%20a%20consulting%20and%20capacity%20building%20initiative%20in%20the%20environment%20and%20climate%20change%20sector.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CInstead%20of%20providing%20finance%20to%20developing%20countries%2C%20affluent%20nations%20have%20exacerbated%20the%20climate%20crisis%20with%20their%20persistent%20investments%20in%20fossil%20fuels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CDeveloping%20countries%20stand%20ready%2C%20awaiting%20the%20necessary%20funds%20to%20safeguard%20their%20people%20against%20imminent%20climate%20disasters.%20Without%20timely%20adaptation%2C%20we%20are%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20unimaginable%20loss%20of%20lives%20and%20livelihoods%20caused%20by%20relentless%20floods%2C%20raging%20wildfires%2C%20and%20surging%20seas%2C%E2%80%9D%20Singh%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fscience.thewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fclimate-change-glossary-every-term-you-need-to-understand-explained%2F%5C%22%3EClimate%20Change%20Glossary%3A%20Every%20Term%20You%20Need%20to%20Understand%2C%20Explained%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EIndia%20and%20the%20adaptation%20gap%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%202023%20Adaptation%20Gap%20Report%20%E2%80%9Creaffirms%E2%80%9D%20what%20countries%20from%20the%20Global%20South%20have%20been%20arguing%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%20now%2C%20that%20the%20%E2%80%9Cgap%20between%20increasing%20climate%20risks%20and%20implemented%20adaptation%20is%20widening%E2%80%9D%2C%20said%20Chandni%20Singh%2C%20one%20of%20the%20lead%20authors%20of%20the%20chapter%20on%20adaptation%20implementation%20in%20this%20year%E2%80%99s%20report.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20gap%20is%20not%20felt%20equally%20%E2%80%93%20it%20impacts%20the%20poorest%20and%20marginalised%20populations%20the%20most%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20wrote%20in%20an%20email%20to%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ci%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cspan%3E.%20%E2%80%9CAnd%20certain%20countries%20face%20a%20wider%20gap%20%E2%80%93%20in%20the%20IPCC%20report%20we%20showed%20how%20countries%20in%20Africa%20and%20South%20and%20Central%20Asia%20see%20the%20widest%20adaptation%20gaps.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20climate%20change-induced%20disasters%20and%20losses%20and%20damages%20are%20growing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20added.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20clear%20signals%20that%20these%20risks%20are%20being%20exacerbated%20by%20inadequate%20mitigation%20of%20greenhouse%20gases%20by%20high%20emitters.%20Further%2C%20finance%20for%20adapting%20to%20these%20escalating%20risks%20is%20a%20trickle%E2%80%A6Building%20climate-resilient%20infrastructure%2C%20developing%20institutional%20capacities%20to%20prepare%20for%20complex%20risk%20management%2C%20and%20%5Benabling%5D%20technical%20innovations%20require%20money%20and%20our%20global%20financing%20mechanisms%20are%20failing%20to%20reach%20the%20most%20vulnerable.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20the%20report%20highlights%20the%20inadequate%20progress%20on%20adaptation%20planning%20and%20implementation%2C%20it%20also%20calls%20for%20an%20increased%20focus%20on%20anticipatory%2C%20just%2C%20and%20effective%20adaptation%20action%20and%20support%2C%20Anjal%20Prakash%2C%20Clinical%20Associate%20Professor%20(Research)%20and%20Research%20Director%2C%20Bharti%20Institute%20of%20Public%20Policy%2C%20Indian%20School%20of%20Business%2C%20told%20Climate%20Trends.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20is%20particularly%20crucial%20for%20a%20country%20like%20India%2C%20which%20faces%20various%20climate%20risks%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Adaptation%20Gap%20Report%202023%20underscores%20the%20critical%20need%20for%20India%20to%20bolster%20its%20climate%20adaptation%20efforts%20and%20calls%20for%20more%20significant%20international%20support%20to%20bridge%20the%20adaptation%20finance%20gap.%20It%20is%20a%20wake-up%20call%20for%20all%20stakeholders%20to%20work%20together%20to%20ensure%20a%20more%20resilient%20and%20sustainable%20future%20for%20India%20and%20the%20world.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698942023000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F11%2F02214750%2Fimage-1468.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdeveloping-countries-are-underfinanced-underprepared-to-adapt-to-climate-change-unep-report%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Adaptation%20Gap%20Report%202023%20finds%20that%20finance%20needs%20for%20developmental%20countries%20are%2010%20to%2018%20times%20as%20high%20as%20the%20current%20international%20public%20adaptation%20finance%20flows.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Fdeveloping-countries-are-underfinanced-underprepared-to-adapt-to-climate-change-unep-report%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22British%20surgeon%20says%20he%20is%20out%20'at%20last'%20after%20spending%20nearly%20a%20month%20trapped%20in%20Gaza%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698941520000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F23%2F11%2F70x70%2Fskynews-abdel-hammas-israel_6345814.jpg%3F20231102174036%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fisrael-hamas-war-british-surgeon-says-he-is-out-at-last-after-spending-nearly-a-month-trapped-in-gaza-12998936%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20British%20surgeon%20who%20was%20trapped%20in%20the%20Gaza%20Strip%20for%20nearly%20a%20month%20after%20the%20conflict%20between%20Israel%20and%20Hamas%20broke%20out%20has%20said%20he%20is%20out%20%26quot%3Bat%20last%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A80%2C