%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Fpolitics-and-nation%2Fsuch-massive-scam-cant-take-place-without-kejriwals-approval-bjp-on-delhi-excise-policy-case%2Farticleshow%2F104849331.cms%5C%22%3Etold%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20press%20that%20the%20action%20against%20AAP%20leaders%2C%20including%20Kejriwal%2C%20is%20part%20of%20a%20legal%20process%20and%20that%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20political%20interests%20have%20nothing%20to%20do%20with%20it.%20He%20attacked%20AAP%20which%2C%20he%20alleged%2C%20has%20been%20caught%20in%20a%20loop%20of%20corrupt%20dealings%20while%20implementing%20the%20excise%20policy.%20Prasad%20said%20that%20the%20case%20exposes%20the%20hollowness%20of%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20anti-corruption%20posturing%2C%20while%20also%20dismissing%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20as%20an%20%E2%80%9Copportunistic%E2%80%9D%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20crux%20of%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20attack%2C%20while%20detailing%20the%20ED%20case%20against%20AAP%20leaders%20in%20the%20excise%20policy%20case%2C%20has%20been%20to%20brand%20the%20Kejriwal-led%20party%20as%20a%20corrupt%20force.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESambit%20Patra%2C%20BJP%20spokesperson%2C%20hammered%20down%20the%20point%20that%20the%20ED%20case%20has%20proven%20that%20AAP%20%E2%80%93%20a%20party%20that%20claimed%20to%20be%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekattar%20imaandaar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(absolutely%20honest)%20%E2%80%93%20has%20been%20exposed%20as%20%E2%80%9C%3Cem%3Ekattar%20beyimaan%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20%3Cem%3Ekattar%20besharam%3C%2Fem%3E%20(absolutely%20corrupt%20and%20shameless)%E2%80%9D.%20Patra%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DWyMmzBlVHQU%5C%22%3Edefended%20that%20the%20summons%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20sent%20to%20Kejriwal%20after%20the%20ED%20had%20taken%20all%20available%20evidence%20into%20account.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20attack%20on%20AAP%20mostly%20hinged%20on%20the%20recent%20Supreme%20Court%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flaw%2Fmanish-sisodia-bail-sc