0after%20the%20INDIA%20bloc%20was%20formed.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKejriwal%20shot%20off%20a%20response%20to%20the%20ED%2C%20urging%20the%20agency%20to%20withdraw%20the%20summons.%20He%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Farvind-kejriwal-enforcement-directorate-raids%5C%22%3Eargued%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20summons%20were%20at%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20behest%2C%20and%20therefore%2C%20were%20%E2%80%9Cillegal%20and%20politically%20motivated%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThereafter%2C%20Rai%20defended%20him%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20ED%E2%80%99s%20letter%20didn%E2%80%99t%20clarify%20whether%20it%20was%20addressed%20to%20the%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20chief%20minister%2C%20or%20AAP%E2%80%99s%20national%20convenor%2C%20or%20Kejriwal%20as%20a%20normal%20citizen.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERai%20said%20that%20it%20was%20clear%20that%20the%20ED%20summons%20were%20at%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20behest%2C%20as%20even%20before%20the%20ED%20had%20responded%20to%20Kejriwal%E2%80%99s%20decision%20to%20skip%20the%20questioning%2C%20the%20BJP%20had%20already%20responded%20at%20the%20agency%E2%80%99s%20behest%20and%20listed%20out%20details%20regarding%20why%20Kejriwal%20was%20summoned.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EKejriwal%2C%20while%20canvassing%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh%E2%80%99s%20Singrauli%2C%20said%20that%20the%20summons%20to%20him%20was%20a%20threat%20that%20he%20keeps%20receiving%20from%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%20quarters.%20He%20added%20that%20AAP%20has%20shown%20that%20it%20was%20possible%20for%20a%20government%20to%20develop%20schools%20and%20better%20healthcare%20for%20the%20poor.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Delhi%20government%20has%20shown%20that%20it%20is%20possible.%20But%20the%20BJP%20will%20not%20do%20any%20such%20thing%20wherever%20it%20is%20in%20power%20nor%20will%20it%20allow%20anyone%20to%20work%20for%20the%20poor%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kejriwal%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EA%20rather%20well-rounded%20criticism%20of%20the%20ED%20summons%20was%20advanced%20by%20Chadha.%20The%20Rajya%20Sabha%20MP%20from%20Punjab%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.indiatoday.in%2Findia%2Fstory%2Farvind-kejriwal-ed-summons-raghav-chadha-delhi-liquor-policy-scam-2456679-2023-11-01%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20summons%20to%20Kejriwal%20was%20a%20possible%20ploy%20to%20eventually%20arrest%20Kejriwal%20to%20wipe%20off%20the%20primary%20opposition%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%2C%20so%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20it%20easy%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20possible%20arrest%20of%20Kejriwal%20will%20be%20the%20first%20in%20a%20%E2%80%9Cseries%20of%20such%20arrests%E2%80%9D%20to%20shut%20out%20the%20top%20leadership%20of%20the%20INDIA%20parties.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20press%20briefing%2C%20he%20said%20that%20after%20the%20arrest%20of%20Kejriwal%2C%20it%20will%20be%20the%20turn%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%2C%20Hemant%20Soren%3B%20deputy%20chief%20minister%20of%20Bihar%2C%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%3B%20top%20leaders%20of%20the%20Trinamool%20Congress%20in%20West%20Bengal%3B%20the%20chief%20minister%20of%20Kerala%2C%20Pinarayi%20Vijayan%3B%20ministers%20in%20the%20M.K.Stalin-led%20Tamil%20Nadu%20government%3B%20and%20big%20opposition%20leaders%20of%20the%20Maha%20Vikas%20Agadi%2C%20the%20opposition%20alliance%20in%20Maharashtra.%20He%20said%20the%20vindictive%20action%20by%20the%20BJP%20will%20also%20be%20taken%20in%20this%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20the%20BJP%20was%20anxious%20after%20the%20opposition%20parties%20decided%20to%20come%20together%20despite%20their%20differences.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EChadha%20said%20that%20if%20INDIA%20becomes%20successful%20in%20fielding%20one%20united%20candidate%20against%20the%20BJP%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%E2%80%99s%20defeat%20is%20certain.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20sources%20gave%20us%20concrete%20inputs%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20hatched%20a%20plan%20to%20arrest%20all%20top%20INDIA%20bloc%20leaders%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20The%20plan%20is%20to%20arrest%20all%20top%20leaders%20of%20INDIA%20parties%2C%20with%20a%20belief%20that%20if%20top%20opposition%20leaders%20are%20in%20prison%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20one%20to%20steer%20the%20opposition%20campaign.%20It%20is%20a%20dangerous%20plan%20that%20violates%20all%20tenets%20of%20democracy%2C%E2%80%9D%20Chadha%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20such%20a%20pattern%20was%20there%20for%20everyone%20to%20see.%20Almost%20all%20top%20opposition%20leaders%20across%20most%20states%2C%20including%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20Sonia%20Gandhi%2C%20Manish%20Sisodia%20and%20Tejashwi%20Yadav%2C%20were%20facing%20different%20unsubstantiated%20charges%2C%20on%20which%20the%20agencies%20initiated%20action%20only%20in%20the%20run-up%20to%20different%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20clear%20that%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20want%20to%20keep%20the%20opposition%20leaders%20busy%20in%20legal%20hassles%20than%20spend%20time%20campaigning%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Fexpress-exclusive%2Fsince-2014-4-fold-jump-in-ed-cases-against-politicians-95-per-cent-are-from-opposition-8163060%2F%5C%22%3E95%25%20of%20the%20ED%20cases%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20have%20been%20against%20opposition%20leaders.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fchronology-samajhiye-5-days-4-agencies-under-modi-govt-control-target-opposition-journalists-activists%5C%22%3EChronology%20Samajhiye%3A%205%20Days%2C%204%20Agencies%20Under%20Modi%20Govt%20Control%20Target%20Opposition%2C%20Journalists%2C%20Activists%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20furore%20over%20the%20summons%20to%20a%20sitting%20chief%20minister%20has%20provoked%20other%20opposition%20parties%20too%20in%20raising%20their%20pitch%20against%20the%20BJP%2C%20an