ompany%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F05%2F16102200%2F38162406612_fd4487d15b_c.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ECERT-In%2C%20the%20nodal%20agency%20that%20deals%20with%20cybersecurity%20threats%2C%20has%20begun%20its%20investigation%20in%20the%20Apple%20threat%20notification%20issue%2C%20and%20a%20notice%20has%20been%20sent%20to%20the%20company%2C%20IT%20secretary%20S.%20Krishnan%20said%20on%20Thursday%20(November%202).%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCERT-In%20has%20started%20its%20probe%E2%80%A6%20they%20(Apple)%20will%20cooperate%20in%20this%20probe%2C%E2%80%9D%20news%20agency%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20reported%20Krishnan%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Feconomictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Findia%2Fnotice-sent-to-apple-cert-in-has-started-probe-it-secretary-on-hacking-attempt-alert-issue%2Farticleshow%2F104907518.cms%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20an%20event%20related%20to%20the%20MeitY-NSF%20research%20collaboration.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20threat%20relates%20to%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Emessage%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%9CApple%20believes%20you%20are%20being%20targeted%20by%20state-sponsored%20attackers%20who%20are%20trying%20to%20remotely%20compromise%20the%20iPhone%20associated%20with%20your%20Apple%20ID%20%E2%80%A6.%E2%80%9D%2C%20which%20was%20sent%20to%20by%20multiple%20opposition%20leaders%2C%20including%20Mahua%20Moitra%2C%20Raghav%20Chadha%2C%20and%20Shashi%20Tharoor.%20It%20was%20also%20sent%20to%20several%20journalists%2C%20including%20Siddharth%20Varadarajan%2C%20founding%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3B%3C%2Fem%3E%20Sriram%20Karri%2C%20resident%20editor%20of%20%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Chronicle%3C%2Fem%3E%3B%20and%20Ravi%20Nair%2C%20journalist%2C%20OCCRP.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20email%20titled%20%E2%80%9CALERT%3A%20State-sponsored%20attackers%20may%20be%20targeting%20your%20iPhone%E2%80%9D%20goes%20on%20to%20say%2C%20%E2%80%9CThese%20attackers%20are%20likely%20targeting%20you%20individually%20because%20of%20who%20you%20are%20or%20what%20you%20do.%20If%20your%20device%20is%20compromised%20by%20a%20state-sponsored%20attacker%2C%20they%20may%20be%20able%20to%20remotely%20access%20your%20sensitive%20data%2C%20communications%2C%20or%20even%20the%20camera%20and%20microphone.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIt%20urges%20the%20recipients%2C%20%E2%80%9CWhile%20it%E2%80%99s%20possible%20this%20is%20a%20false%20alarm%2C%20please%20take%20this%20warning%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20October%2031%2C%20Apple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Esaid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CApple%20does%20not%20attribute%20the%20threat%20notifications%20to%20any%20specific%20state-sponsored%20attacker.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThese%20threat%20notifications%20were%20enabled%20by%20the%20company%20in%202021%2C%20and%20since%20then%20such%20notifications%20have%20reportedly%20been%20sent%20to%20individuals%20in%20nearly%20150%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFollowing%20opposition%20MPs%E2%80%99%20claims%20of%20receiving%20these%20hacking%20attempt%20warnings%2C%20IT%20Minister%20Ashwini%20Vaishnaw%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Findia%2Fgovt-orders-probe-after-opposition-mps-claims-of-receiving-hacking-attempt-warnings-from-apple%2Fcid%2F1976648%5C%22%3Eissued%20a%20statement%20saying%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20government%20takes%20its%20role%20of%20protecting%20the%20privacy%20and%20security%20of%20all%20citizens%20very%20seriously.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20notification%20about%20%E2%80%98state-sponsored%20attacks%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9Cseems%20vague%20and%20non-specific%20in%20nature%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20week%2C%20the%20Minister%20of%20State%20for%20Electronics%20and%20IT%20Rajeev%20Chandrasekhar%20had%20said%20that%20the%20government%20wants%20Apple%20to%20clarify%20if%20its%20devices%20are%20secure%20and%20why%20%E2%80%98threat%20notifications%E2%80%99%20were%20sent%20to%20people%20in%20over%20150%20countries%2C%20given%20the%20company%E2%80%99s%20repeated%20claims%20about%20its%20products%20being%20designed%20for%20privacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20the%20names%20in%20the%20hacking%20attempt%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fapple-india-state-sponsored-spyware%5C%22%3Elist%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20well-known%20people%20who%20are%20open%20critics%20of%20the%20Narendra%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20questions%20raised%20in%20this%20matter%20are%20a%20source%20of%20concern%2C%20as%20per%20many%20experts%2C%20who%20refocused%20attention%20on%20the%202021%20Pegasus%20Project%20that%20revealed%20that%20over%20a%20dozen%20phones%20in%20India%2C%20belonging%20to%20politicians%2C%20journalists%2C%20human%20rights%20activists%2C%20and%20others%2C%20were%20infected%20with%20Israeli%20spyware.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20members%20whose%20phones%20were%20infected%20with%20the%20spyware%20included%20then%20Congress%20president%20Rahul%20Gandhi%2C%20lawyers%2C%20a%20sitting%20judge%2C%20an%20election%20commissioner%2C%20the%20ousted%20CBI%20director%20and%20family%20members%20of%20such%20persons%20also%2C%20just%20before%20and%20after%20the%20previous%20general%20elections%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court-appointed%20committee%20investigating%20this%20matter%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Findianexpress.com%2Farticle%2Findia%2Fsupreme-court-pegasus-spyware-case-8110566%2F%5C%22%3Enoted%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20did%20not%20cooperate%20with%20its%20investigation%2C%20while%20adding%20that%20it%20found%20no%20conclusive%20evidence%20of%20spyware%20use%20in%20the%20examined%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20panel%20had%20submitted%20it