0Wang%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20went%20to%20great%20lengths%20to%20convince%20the%20two%20women%2C%20showcasing%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20credible%20patent%20documents%20and%20prestigious%20awards%20certificates%20for%20his%20cancer%20treatment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EFilled%20with%20hope%2C%20Ms%20Wang's%20mother%20immediately%20purchased%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20liquid%20medication%20from%20Mr%20Yu%20at%20a%20cost%20of%2020%2C000%20yuan%20(US%242%2C700)%2C%20which%20he%20assured%20was%20a%20simple%20oral%20remedy.%20Over%20the%20course%20of%20a%20year%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said%20she%20and%20her%20mother%20flew%20to%20Wuhan%20from%20their%20home%20in%20northeastern%20Liaoning%20province%20six%20times.%20This%20journey%20took%20a%20severe%20financial%20toll%2C%20with%20the%20total%20expenditure%20racing%20over%20200%2C000%20yuan.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20giving%20the%20elderly%20woman%20oral%20medication%2C%20Mr%20Yu%20also%20made%20dozens%20of%20injections%20into%20her%20breasts%20to%20make%20her%20lose%20blood%2C%20Ms%20Wang%20said%2C%20as%20per%20the%20outlet.%20He%20bizarrely%20also%20told%20the%20woman%20to%20apply%20a%20mixture%20of%20cement%20and%20lime%20skin%20under%20her%20armpits%2C%20claiming%20that%20it%20would%20aid%20in%20shrinking%20the%20cancerous%20lumps.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20told%20my%20mother%20to%20apply%20cement%20mixed%20with%20lime%20on%20the%20skin%20under%20her%20armpits%2C%20saying%20this%20could%20help%20shrink%20lumps.%20My%20mother%20followed%20his%20instructions%20but%20her%20skin%20festered%20after%20doing%20it%20for%20two%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Wang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAlso%20Read%20%7C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fus-man-arrested-for-pointing-gun-at-6-year-old-boys-head-over-halloween-candy-bag-4536390%5C%22%3EUS%20Man%20Arrested%20For%20Pointing%20Gun%20At%206-Year-Old%20Boy's%20Head%20Over%20Halloween%20Candy%20Bag%3C%2F