oth%20formats.%20He%20is%20the%20first%20player%20to%20hit%20an%20ODI%20double%20hundred%20and%20to%20have%20played%20200%20Test%20matches.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20has%20201%20international%20wickets%20to%20his%20name%2C%20making%20him%20a%20very%20useful%20part-time%20spin%20bowling%20option.%20With%20a%20total%20of%20664%20international%20appearances%2C%20he%20is%20the%20most-capped%20player%20of%20all%20time.%20He%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20Team%20which%20won%20the%20ICC%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20in%202011.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin%20has%20played%20six%20IPL%20seasons%20from%202008-2013%2C%20all%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%2C%20where%20he%20has%20scored%20a%20total%20of%202334%20runs%20in%2078%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2034.84.%20Sachin%20has%2013%20fifties%20and%20one%20hundred%20under%20his%20belt%2C%20hitting%2029%20sixes%20and%20295%20fours%20with%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20119.82.%20He%20won%20the%202013%20edition%20of%20the%20tournament%20with%20the%20franchise%20as%20a%20player.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ESachin's%20best%20performance%20came%20in%20IPL%202010.%20He%20scored%20618%20runs%20in%2015%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2047.53%20at%20a%20strike%20rate%20of%20132.61.%20He%20scored%20five%20fifties%20that%20season%20and%20his%20best%20individual%20score%20was%2089*.%20He%20won%20the%20'Orange%20Cap'%20that%20season.%20MI%20finished%20as%20runners-up%20that%20season.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EWith%20ANI%20inputs%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698847380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fhjl8ti4g_sachin-wc_625x300_01_November_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ficc-cricket-world-cup-2023%2Fsachin-tendulkars-statue-unveiled-at-wankhede-stadium-where-india-won-the-2011-cricket-world-cup-watch-4535912%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Sachin%20Tendulkar's%20life-sized%20statue%20has%20unveiled%20at%20the%20Wankhede%20Stadium%20on%20the%20eve%20of%20India's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202023%20clash%20