d%20an%20off-grid%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F269780%2Fmy-zero-waste-home-saves-70-energy-by-using-the-sun-to-run-appliances%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esolar%20power%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewith%20a%20capacity%20of%20one%20kilowatt%20to%20fulfil%20the%20household%E2%80%99s%20essential%20energy%20requirements.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20the%20family%20has%20successfully%20reduced%20their%20monthly%20electricity%20bill%20from%20Rs%20800%20to%20a%20mere%20Rs%2080.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20he%20annually%20collects%2040%2C000%20litres%20of%20rainwater%20and%20redirects%20an%20excess%20of%20three%20lakh%20litres%20to%20recharge%20the%20borewell.%20After%20filtering%20water%20through%20sand%20filters%2C%20the%20family%20ensures%20the%20water%E2%80%99s%20purity%2C%20allowing%20them%20to%20use%20it%20for%20drinking%20purposes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixed%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fsustainable-home-3-1698759604-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333372%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBharani%20has%20also%20made%20unique%20bricks%20from%20styrofoam%20by%20mixing%20it%20with%20cement.%20Close%20to%2070%20percent%20of%20the%20brick%20is%20made%20from%20scrap.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98We%20make%20our%20own%20chemical-free%20home%20products%E2%80%99%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20rainwater%20harvesting%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20has%20implemented%20a%20greywater%20treatment%20system%2C%20which%20effectively%20repurposes%20treated%20greywater%20from%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20basins%2C%20and%20bathrooms%20for%20watering%20the%20plants%20in%20their%20garden.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20we%20encountered%20a%20foul%20smell%20coming%20from%20nearby%20tanks%2C%20mostly%20from%20the%20accumulated%20dirty%20water.%20We%20realised%20that%20the%20smell%20was%20mostly%20because%20of%20the%20various%20oils%20and%20chemical%20detergents%20we%20used%2C%20which%20polluted%20the%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%20adding%20that%20this%20set%20them%20to%20start%20another%20exciting%20experiment.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInstead%20of%20chemical%20cleaners%2C%20Ramachandrudu%20started%20making%20natural%20cleaners%20using%20a%20blend%20of%20bio%20enzymes%2C%20cow%20dung%2C%20and%20wood%20ash.%20To%20create%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F332396%2Fhow-to-make-bio-enzymes-from-kitchen-waste-at-home-diy-steps-by-kolkata-gardener-nita-singh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebio%20enzymes%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20collects%20flowers%20and%20lime%20waste%2C%20adding%20natural%20ingredients%20such%20as%20fenugreek%2C%20coconut%2C%20rice%2C%20aloe%20vera%2C%20black%20seeds%2C%20and%20hibiscus.%20These%20elements%20are%20combined%20to%20make%20powerful%20shampoos%2C%20body%20washes%20and%20liquid%20cleaners%20for%20washing%20clothes.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20completely%20stopped%20purchasing%20detergents%20from%20the%20market%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThroughout%20these%20years%2C%20the%20father-son%20duo%20embarked%20on%20their%20transformative%20journey%20without%20a%20clear%20plan.%20Rather%2C%20each%20experiment%20served%20as%20a%20catalyst%20for%20the%20next%2C%20leading%20to%20several%20compelling%20and%20innovative%20projects.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ERamachandrudu%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20am%20glad%20my%20home%20gave%20me%20an%20opportunity%20to%20implement%20my%20ideas%20and%20transition%20from%20advising%20others%20to%20actually%20doing%20something.%20Although%20physically%20exhausting%2C%20it%20has%20brought%20a%20lot%20of%20satisfaction%20my%20way%2C%20both%20at%20the%20professional%20and%20personal%20levels.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20photos%3A%20Bharani%20and%20Nemani)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESource%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.mdpi.com%2F2071-1050%2F14%2F21%2F14393%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESustainability%20Considerations%20of%20Green%20Buildings%3A%20A%20Detailed%20Overview%20on%20Current%20Advancements%20and%20Future%20Considerations%3A%20%3C%2Fa%3EPublished%20in%20MDPI%20on%203%20November%202022.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698760856000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D333339%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Located%20in%20Hyderabad%2C%20father-son%20duo%20M%20V%20Ramachandradu%20and%20Bharani%20have%20built%20a%20solar-powered%20sustainable%20home%20out%20of%20shipping%20containers.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A107%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F333339%2Fhyderabad-sustainable-home-made-of-shipping-containers-harvest-rainwater-solar-energy%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Building%20Scale%20With%20Zero%20Middlemen%3A%20How%20Small-Scale%20Farmers%20In%20Bihar%20Double%20Their%20Income%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20Bayer%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20year%202018%20marked%20a%20watershed%20moment%20for%20Bhagalpur%20district%20in%20Bihar.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F289539%2Fchennai-entrepreneur-makes-waterproof-wood-from-rice-husk-to-build-furniture%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EKatarni%20rice%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20short-grained%20variety%2C%20known%20for%20its%20unique%20taste%20and%20aroma%2C%20along%20with%20the%20Jardalu%20mango%20native%20to%20the%20region%2C%20received%20the%20coveted%20Geographical%20Indication%20(GI)%20tag%20from%20the%20UN%20%E2%80%94%20a%20distinction%20that%20promised%20to%20breathe%20new%20life%20into%20the%20agricultural%20landscape%20of%20Bihar.%20While%20this%20recognition%20was%20an%20auspicious%20beginning%2C%20challenges%20persisted%20for%20small-scale%20farmers%2C%20who%20struggled%20to%20maximise%20their%20profits%20and%20access%20broader%20markets.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Manish%20Singh%2C%20a%20teacher%20by%20profession%2C%20hailing%20from%20a%20farming%20family%20in%20Sultangunj%20village%20in%20Bhagalpur%2C%20decided%20to%20take%20the%20plunge%20into%20agriculture.%20With%20a%20deep-rooted%20passion%20for%20farming%20and%20a%20vision%20to%20amplify%20the%20value%20of%20the%20produce%2C%20Manish%20embarked%20on%20a%20mission.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EDespite%20having%20a%20GI%20tag%2C%20most%20farmers%20in%20the%20district%20were%20selling%20Katarni%20paddy%20at%20Rs%2030%20per%20kg.%20The%20challenge%2C%20Manish%20says%2C%20was%20that%20%E2%80%9Cfarmers%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20the%20value%20of%20the%20rice.%20Since%20we%20are%20all%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20were%20not%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20price%20or%20find%20the%20right%20people%20to%20sell%20our%20products%20to.%E2%80%9D%20He%20knew%20collectivisation%20was%20the%20only%20way%20to%20ensure%20that%20farmers%20like%20himself%20are%20able%20to%20get%20the%20right%20value%20for%20their%20produce%2C%20Manish%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EManish%20led%20a%20group%20of%20farmers%20to%20form%20the%20Jardalu%20and%20Katarni%20Agro%20Producer%20Company%20Limited%2C%20a%20Farmer%20Producer%20Organisation%20(FPO)%2C%20in%20April%202023.%20Their%20journey%20was%20made%20possible%20through%20the%20support%20of%20Bayer%2C%20working%20in%20collaboration%20with%20the%20Small%20Farmers%E2%80%99%20Agri-Business%20Consortium%20(SFAC)%20under%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20government%20developed%20the%20concept%20of%20FPOs%20in%20the%20early%202000s%20to%20enable%20small%20and%20marginal%20farmers%20to%20improve%20their%20access%20to%20investments%2C%20technology%2C%20and%20markets.%20The%20power%20of%20collectivisation%20not%20only%20improved%20production%20efficiency%20but%20also%20paved%20the%20way%20for%20better%20pricing%20strategies%20and%20marketing%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHelping%20farmers%20become%20self-reliant%3C%2Fh2%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%202560px)%20100vw%2C%202560px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%222560%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Bayer%20nurtures%20and%20guides%20FPOs%20in%2021%20states%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2Fbayer1-min-1698759017-scaled.jpeg%20