0programme%20%E2%80%94%20has%20propelled%20the%20movement%20in%20a%20short%20span%20of%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20%E2%80%98Nanhi%20Kali%20after-school%20tuition%20centres%E2%80%99%20are%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F261243%2Fmalnutrition-orphanage-girl-child-hyderabad-women-donation%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emanaged%20by%20a%20young%20woman%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20same%20community%20as%20the%20girls.%20When%20sports%20were%20introduced%2C%20these%20tutors%20were%20to%20deliver%20the%20weekly%20sports%20drills%20and%20practices.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20the%20first%20year%20it%20was%20optional%20for%20tutors%20to%20become%20%E2%80%98sports%20allies%E2%80%99.%20About%20half%20of%20them%20said%20that%20they%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20it%20because%20they%20didn%E2%80%99t%20know%20what%20it%20was.%20By%20the%20second%20year%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20Rohini%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20tutors%20initially%20went%20in%20not%20knowing%20what%20to%20expect%2C%20but%20once%20they%20experienced%20it%2C%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20event%2C%20back%20in%202020%2C%20vindicated%20their%20belief%20about%20the%20benefits%20of%20sports%20and%20physical%20activity%2C%20and%20it%20was%20a%20result%20of%20the%20organisation%20inculcating%20sports%20into%20their%20work%20and%20regular%20programming.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20videos%20and%20photos%20of%20the%20girls%20doing%20these%20sports%20drills%20were%20sent%20back%20and%20forth%20over%20WhatsApp%20to%20the%20sports%20allies.%20To%20streamline%20this%20process%20further%2C%20Naandi%20decided%20to%20create%20its%20own%20app%20called%20SportStar%20to%20create%20a%20database.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20once%20a%20week%2C%20a%20video%20of%20a%20sports%20drill%20is%20sent%20out%20to%20roughly%206%2C000%20sports%20allies.%20This%20allows%20for%20feedback%20and%20collaboration%20among%20all%20of%20them%20as%20everyone%20shares%20their%20training%20videos%2C%20which%20ensures%20that%20the%20app%20has%20more%20content%20for%20their%20perusal.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20girls%20cannot%20relate%20to%20YouTube%20videos%20of%20foreigners%20doing%20these%20drills.%20With%20this%20exchange%20of%20videos%2C%20we%20have%20ended%20up%20creating%20more%20resources%20for%20our%20girls%20to%20imbibe%20information%20from.%20The%20app%20is%20not%20open%20to%20the%20public%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Rohini.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20a%20girl%20is%20doing%20some%20exercise%20well%2C%20then%20we%20use%20that%20video%20during%20our%20drills%20across%20the%20country%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%20This%20is%20what%20the%20organisation%20terms%20%E2%80%98Sports%20for%20Life%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20960px)%20100vw%2C%20960px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Every%20young%20girl%20now%20enjoys%20one%20sports%20class%20per%20week%20where%20they%20not%20only%20play%20but%20also%20learn%20about%20body%20movement%2C%20nutrition%20and%20menstrual%20health%20management.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921.jpg%20960w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F142223116_10158970115872378_6100513293125282098_n-1698680921-768x576.jpg%20768w%