Cp%3EAnd%20she%20was%20doing%20all%20this%20at%20a%20time%20when%20conservation%2C%20and%20especially%20field%20conservation%2C%20was%20almost%20entirely%20an%20exclusively%20male%20domain.%20In%20her%20younger%20days%2C%20she%20was%20working%20in%20forests%20that%20were%20hardly%20visited%20by%20any%20naturalist%2C%20much%20less%20anyone%20worrying%20about%20their%20conservation.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3EHer%20work%20could%20range%20from%20charting%20up%20a%20management%20plan%20for%20a%20single%20forest%20to%20working%20in%20framing%20a%20nationwide%20policy%20as%20she%20did%20during%20her%20years%20in%20the%20Tiger%20Task%20Force%20or%20as%20an%20important%20member%20involved%20in%20the%20framing%20of%20the%20Wildlife%20(Protection)%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22During%20her%20life%2C%20Anne%20Wright%20received%20a%20myriad%20of%20awards%20for%20her%20conservation%20work.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2FAnne-Wright-Award-1698675452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-333245%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EDuring%20her%20life%2C%20Anne%20Wright%20received%20a%20myriad%20of%20awards%20for%20her%20conservation%20work.%20She%20was%20awarded%20the%20Order%20of%20Golden%20Ark%20by%20Prince%20Bernhard%20of%20Netherlands%20in%201979%2C%20%E2%80%98Most%20Excellent%20Order%20of%20the%20British%20Empire%E2%80%99%20(MBE)%20in%201983%2C%20and%20the%20Sanctuary%20Asia%20Lifetime%20Service%20Award%20in%202013.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20what%20strikes%20out%20the%20most%20to%20me%20is%20her%20ability%20to%20forge%20alliances%20over%20common%20cause%20across%20an%20incredibly%20diverse%20set%20of%20people%20and%20stakeholders%20%E2%80%94%20from%20forest%20officers%20to%20politicians%20in%20high%20offices%3B%20from%20businessmen%20to%20communities%20living%20around%20forests%3B%20from%20celebrities%20and%20global%20and%20national%20public%20figures%20to%20young%20school%20kids%3B%20and%20from%20naturalists%20to%20policymakers.%20She%20worked%20with%20everyone%20and%20brought%20them%20together%20for%20the%20cause%20of%20conservation%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Raza.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20can%20think%20of%20very%20few%20people%2C%20perhaps%20none%2C%20in%20India%E2%80%99s%20conservation%20history%20who%20single-handedly%20worked%20over%20such%20a%20long%20period%2C%20over%20so%20many%20states%2C%20and%20with%20so%20many%20diverse%20sets%20of%20peoples%20and%20interests%20in%20such%20harmony%2C%20and%20brought%20about%20such%20remarkable%20results.%20And%20of%20course%20who%20can%20forget%20the%20power%20of%20her%20pen%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%20%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20Images%20courtesy%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FRazaKazmi17%2Fstatus%2F1710262197698310376%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERaza%20Kazmi%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Wildlife%20Protection%20Society%20of%20India%20(WPSI)%2FFacebook%20and%20Kipling%20Camp%2FFacebook)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1698676639000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22